Ya ce aikin ya wuce karfin gwamnatin yankin.
Ya kara da cewa, yanzu haka ya kai rahoton lamarin ga hukumar kula da gaggawa ta jihar Kebbi (KSEMA), wanda ya nemi a tura musu sunayen masu gidajen da abin ya shafa.
Majiyoyi sun shaida wa LEADERSHIP TODAY cewa da yawa daga cikin wadanda suka rasa gidajensu yanzu sun yi hijira zuwa Jamhuriyar Nijar, saboda kasashen suna kusa da juna, hanya ce kawai ta raba garuruwan, amma akwai kyakkyawar alakar zamantakewa da kuma aure tsakanin su.
