Na yi alkawarin cika burin Buhari - Magashi - Jaridun Hausa
Ministan tsaron Najeriya, Manjo Janar Bashir Salihi Magashi (rtd), ya yi alkawarin cika burin Shugaba Muhammadu Buhari na tabbatar da cewa gwamnatinsa ta kawo karshen rikicin tsaro a duk fadin tarayya.
An sanar da wannan a cikin wata sanarwa da Ministan ya fitar a Abuja a lokacin da ya cika shekara guda a kan kujerar, wanda Mataimakinsa na Bayanai, Mohammad Abdulkadir ya sanya hannu.
Ya ce zai yi hakan ne saboda Buhari a matsayinsa na babban kwamandan sojojin Najeriya, ya sadaukar da rayuwarsa ga kasar ba tare da son kai ba.
Janar Magashi ya kuma gode wa Shugaba Buhari da ya ba shi damar yi wa kasarsa hidima, yana mai cewa yanzu sun fara aiki tukuru domin Najeriya da 'yan Najeriya.
Yayin da yake sake tabbatar da goyon bayan shugaban ga dakarun kasar, don kawo karshen kalubalen tsaro da 'yan tawaye, sace-sacen mutane da kuma wadanda ke dogara da bindigogi, Janar Magashi ya nuna kwarin gwiwa cewa hasken da ke nuna karshen wadannan matsalolin yana kan hanya.
Ya yi kira ga dukkan shugabannin tsaron Najeriya da su tashi tsaye su nuna kishin kasa, ya kara da cewa su ci gaba da aiki tare, kamar yadda hakkin dukkan 'yan Najeriya ne su yi.
A karshe ya gode wa rundunar sojin Najeriya da dukkan masu ruwa da tsaki a harkokin tsaron Najeriya saboda goyon bayan da suka nuna a lokacin da yake kwanaki 365 a ofis.
An Yi Tawaye a Amirka a Kan Rashin Adalci na Kabila
Masu zanga-zanga sun fito kan titunan birane da dama na Amurka don jawo hankali ga rashin adalci na launin fata.
Zanga-zangar a Portland, Oregon, ta kasance har tsawon watanni biyu, tun mutuwar George Floyd a ranar 25 ga Mayu yayin da yake tsare a Minneapolis, Minnesota.
Gwamnatin Trump ta tura jami'an tarayya zuwa Portland, suna kara karin man fetur ga zanga-zangar.
Masu zanga-zangar yanzu suna kuma zanga-zangar nuna rashin amincewarsu da kasancewar gwamnatin tarayya a birnin.
A Seattle, 'yan sanda ta amfani da fashewar wuta da hayaki mai sa hawaye sun kama mutane 45 a ranar Asabar bayan zanga-zangar goyon baya ko zanga-zangar a Portland ta zama ta tashin hankali.
'Yan sanda sun ce an jikkata jami'an 'yan sanda sama da 20.
A ranar Asabar da dare, a Austin, Texas, an kashe wani mutum lokacin da wani ya harbe wani motsi na Black Lives Matter.
Rahotanni a kafafen yada labarai sun ce mutumin na iya kusantar wata mota da bindiga kafin a harbe shi.
"Duk abin da na sani shi ne cewa wani ya mutu yayin zanga-zanga abin ban tsoro ne", in ji Magajin garin Austin Steve Adler a cikin wata sanarwa.
Adler ya ce "zuciyarsa ta ɓaci kuma ya yi mamaki".
A Louisville, Kentucky, wata kungiya ta masu zanga-zangar dauke da makamai ta bukaci a yi adalci ga Breonna Taylor, wata bakar fata da ta mutu a Louisville lokacin da 'yan sanda suka shiga gidanta ba tare da gargadi ba a kan umarnin "ba ƙwanƙwasawa" kuma suka harbe ta.
Saurayin Taylor ya fara harbi jami'an, yana zaton sun shiga cikin gida.
An kori wani jami'in 'yan sanda saboda lamarin Taylor, amma ba a tuhumi sauran jami'an ba.
Shugaban kungiyar NFAC, wata kungiyar 'yan bindiga ta baki da ke cikin zanga-zangar, ya ce yana son binciken da 'yan sanda ke yi kan kisan Taylor ya zama mai haske.
'Yan sanda sun ce an raunata 'yan NFAC uku a ranar Asabar lokacin da wani makami na mayakan ya yi harbi ba da gangan ba.
Rahotanni sun ce Amurka ta kara matsa lamba kan masu aikin kwangila na Nord Stream 2 - RT Business News
Gwamnatin Amurka ta sake yin wasu kokarin tilasta wa kamfanonin Turai su yi watsi da aikin bututun gas na Nord Stream 2 da Rasha ke jagoranta, Welt am Sonntag ta ruwaito, tana ambaton mutanen da ke da masaniya game da tattaunawar kan batun.
A cewar jaridar, jami'an ma'aikatar harkokin wajen Amirka da ma'aikatar baitulmalin Amirka da kuma ma'aikatar makamashi sun tuntubi 'yan kwangila na Turai don su tabbata cewa sun fahimci sakamakon ci gaba da aikin.
An bayar da rahoton cewa jami'ai goma sha biyu sun gudanar da aƙalla taron kan layi biyu tare da wakilan kamfanonin a cikin 'yan kwanakin nan.
Da yake magana a cikin "abokantaka", bangaren Amurka ya jaddada cewa yana son hana kammala aikin Nord Stream 2, masu lura da tattaunawar ta yanar gizo sun ce.
"Na yi imanin barazanar tana da matukar tsanani", in ji daya daga cikinsu ga jaridar Jamus.
Wadannan barazanar sun yi daidai da kalaman Sakataren Harkokin Wajen Amurka Mike Pompeo a makon da ya gabata, inda ya yi gargadin cewa kamfanonin da ke cikin aikin sun fi kyau "su fita yanzu" ko kuma suna fuskantar hukunci a karkashin Sashe na 232 na sanannen Dokar Cin Zarafin Abokan adawar Amurka ta hanyar Takunkumi (CAATSA).
Baya ga babbar kamfanin samar da makamashi na Rasha, Gazprom, wanda ke ci gaba da aikin, kamfanoni biyar na Turai sun shiga.
Waɗannan su ne Engie na Faransa, OMV na Austriya, kamfanin Royal Dutch Shell na Birtaniya da Netherlands, da kuma Wintershall da Uniper na Jamus.
Da yake magana da Welt am Sonntag, wannan na ƙarshe ya kira ƙoƙarin Amurka na lalata "babban aikin samar da kayayyakin more rayuwa" a matsayin sa baki a kan ikon mallakar Turai.
A farkon wannan makon, Majalisar Wakilai ta Amurka ta amince da wani gyara ga Dokar Ba da Izini na Tsaro na Kasa, wanda ke nufin faɗaɗa takunkumin Amurka kan kamfanonin da ke da hannu wajen shigar da bututun gas na Nord Stream 2 na Rasha.
A cewar daya daga cikin masu daukar nauyin kudurin, matakan na iya zama masu nufin kamfanonin da ke samar da jiragen ruwa, inshora, wuraren tashar jiragen ruwa, ko kuma ayyukan da ke tattare da wadannan jiragen ruwa, da kuma wadanda ke samar da takardar shaida ga Nord Stream 2.
Kasuwancin Turai da jami'an gwamnati sun yi Allah wadai da yunkurin Amurka na tsoma baki a siyasar makamashi ta Turai ta hanyar sanya takunkumi kan Nord Stream 2, wasu ma sun bukaci Brussels ta yi aiki kan matakan magance matsalar.
Moscow ma ta yi tir da matakin Washington, tana mai cewa gasa ce mara kyau.
A farkon wannan makon, kakakin shugaban kasar Dmitry Peskov ya ce Rasha za ta samar da sabon dabarun kammala aikin idan Washington ta ci gaba da sabbin matakan hukuntawa.
