Sautunan ƙaramin fashewar abubuwa da aka maimaita sun yi sauti a titunan birnin a jihar Washington, kuma hayaki ya tashi daga wani yanki inda masu zanga-zangar suka ƙone tirela a wurin ginin cibiyar tsare matasa.
Masu zanga-zangar sun sare tayoyin motoci da kuma fasa tagogin tirela.
