Za a Bada izinin mutane 50 a Masallatai a Eid, Babu Sallar Jama'a a Eidgah: Karnataka
Za a yi bikin Eid-ul-Azha, wanda kuma aka fi sani da Bakrid, a ranar 31 ga Yuli da 1 ga Agusta.
Gwamnatin Karnataka ta ba da izinin sallar Eid-ul-Azha kawai a masallatai tare da mutane 50 a lokaci guda kuma ta ce an hana sallar jama'a a Eidgah da sauran wurare saboda annobar coronavirus.
Mutanen da ke ziyartar masallatai don sallah dole ne su sanya abin rufe fuska da kiyaye nesa, Sakataren Kula da 'Yan tsiraru da Sakataren Wakf AB Ibrahim ya ce a cikin umarni.
Ya ce kwamitin Hilal ya yanke shawarar cewa za a yi bikin Eid-ul-Azza, wanda kuma ake kira Bakrid, a ranar 31 ga Yuli a gundumar Udupi, Dakshina Kannada da Kodagu yayin da za a yi shi a ranar 1 ga Agusta a sauran jihar.
Da yake lura da cewa sallar jama'a tana daya daga cikin muhimman ayyukan da musulmai ke yi a lokacin Bakrid, umarnin ya ce saboda annobar COVID-19 an hana irin waɗannan abubuwan a Eidgah da sauran wurare.
Koyaya, za a ba da izinin yin addu'o'i a cikin masallatai tare da ƙuntatawa cewa ba za a iya samun mutane sama da 50 ba.
Idan akwai mutane da yawa, ya kamata a yi sallar a rukuni, sashen ya ce a cikin umarnin.
Bai kamata a yi addu'o'in taro a wasu wurare kamar zauren taro, gine-ginen al'umma da "Shadi Mahal" ba, "in ji umarnin.
Karnataka ta ba da izinin buɗe haikalin, masallatai da sauran wuraren bauta don masu ibada daga 8 ga Yuni tare da duk matakan rigakafin COVID-19.
Kungiyar yunwa ta kori Yoho bayan lamarin da ya faru a fadar shugaban kasa
WASHINGTON (AP) - Wata kungiya mai zaman kanta ta Kirista wacce ke neman kawo karshen yunwa ta ce a ranar Asabar ta nemi kuma ta karbi murabus din wakilin Ted Yoho daga kwamitin gudanarwar ta sakamakon abin da ta kira "harshen magana" kan wakilin Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez.
Ocasio-Cortez, D-N.Y., ta zargi Yoho, R-Fla., da yin amfani da cin mutunci da cin zarafin mata yayin da yake tsawata mata a lokacin da aka yi ta fama a ranar Litinin da ta gabata a kan matakan Capitol.
Yoho ya ci gaba da cewa bai yi amfani da kalmomin da aka ambata ba, kodayake wani mai rahoto wanda ya shaida lamarin ya tabbatar da harshen kamar yadda ta bayyana shi.
A cikin wata sanarwa, Gurasa don Duniya ta ce kwamitin ta ya gana da Yoho ranar Juma'a kuma ya nemi ya yi murabus "a matsayin wani mataki da ya sake tabbatar da jajircewarmu na kasancewa tare da mata da mutanen fata, a kasa da duniya, yayin da suke ci gaba da jagorantar mu zuwa duniya mai yawan wariyar launin fata da adalci".
A shafin yanar gizonta, Gurasa don Duniya ta ce "muryar kirista ta gama gari" tana matsawa Majalisa da gwamnati don kawo karshen yunwa a kasa da duniya.
"A matsayin kungiyar Kirista mai bangarori biyu da ke da niyyar rage yunwa da talauci ta hanyar manufofin jama'a masu kyau, Gurasa don Duniya tana tallafawa dabi'un girmamawa, mutunci, da jinƙai da Yesu ya kira mu lokacin da muke shiga masu yanke shawara daga duk bangarorin siyasa", in ji sanarwar.
"Mun yi imanin cewa ayyukan da 'yan jarida suka ruwaito na Ted Yoho ba su nuna ka'idodin dabi'un da ake tsammani daga mambobin kwamitinmu ba".
Wani mai magana da yawun Yoho bai amsa imel din da aka aiko masa ba.
A wani jawabi na musamman ranar Alhamis a majalisar, Ocasio-Cortez ta ba da labarin abin da ya faru kuma ta fadada maganganunta don kai hari ga abin da ta kira al'adun jinsi na "karɓar tashin hankali da kuma lalata mata".
Sama da abokan aiki goma sha biyu sun hada kai da ita wajen bayyana lamarin a matsayin halin maza na yau da kullun.
Yoho ya bayyana ganawar a matsayin taƙaitaccen tattaunawar siyasa kuma ya ce "ba a kusanci kowa ba, ba a zalunta shi, ko kuma a kai masa hari".
Ya yi nadama don "taurin kansa".
Ocasio-Cortez, mai shekara 30, 'yar makaranta ce mai ci gaba wacce ta sami yabo da suka saboda fitowarta.
Yoho, mai shekara 65, daya daga cikin 'yan majalisa masu ra'ayin mazan jiya, zai yi ritaya a karshen wa'adinsa na hudu.
