Wilfried Zaha na son barin Crystal Palace, Roy Hodgson ya ce: "Ku kula da wannan sararin samaniya"
Kocin Crystal Palace Roy Hodgson ya yi wa magoya baya mummunan rauni kafin kakar wasa ta bayyana cewa tauraron dan wasan gaba Wilf Zaha yana son barin kulob din.
