Malaysia na neman 'yan Rohingya 24 da ake fargabar sun nutse a tsibirin
KUALA LUMPUR, Malaysia (AP) - Hukumomin Malaysia sun ce a ranar Lahadi suna neman 'yan gudun hijirar Rohingya da dama da ake fargabar sun nutse bayan tsalle daga jirgin ruwan su a tsibirin Langkawi da ke arewacin kasar.
Zawawi Abdullah, babban jami'in hukumar kula da ayyukan ruwa ta Malaysia, ya ce bayanan farko na 'yan sanda sun nuna cewa mutum daya ne kawai daga cikin maza 25 na Rohingya da suka yi tsalle daga jirgin ruwan ya yi iyo zuwa gabar teku.
Wanda ya tsira shi kadai ya nemi taimakon 'yan sanda a daren Asabar kuma an tsare shi don ci gaba da bincike, in ji Zawawi.
Daruruwan dubban musulmai 'yan kabilar Rohingya sun tsere daga Myanmar saboda hare-haren da sojoji ke kai musu, kuma da yawa daga cikinsu suna zaune ne a sansanonin 'yan gudun hijira da ke Bangladesh.
Malaysia da Musulmai suka fi rinjaye ta kasance wurin da jiragen ruwa da masu fataucin mutane suka shirya suke zuwa da yawa, waɗanda suke yi wa 'yan gudun hijirar alkawarin samun rayuwa mafi kyau a ƙasashen waje.
Zawawi ya ce an tura jiragen ruwa biyu da jirgin sama guda a binciken.
Ya ce hukumar za ta kuma gargadi masunta na gida da hukumomi a makwabciyar Thailand don taimakawa wajen binciken.
Bai bayar da karin bayani game da jirgin ba.
A watan jiya, hukumomin Malaysia sun kama 'yan gudun hijirar Rohingya 269 kuma sun gano gawarwakin da ke cikin jirgin da ake zargi da safarar mutane a Langkawi wanda suka ce an lalata shi da gangan don kada a sake mayar da shi cikin teku.
Hukumar Kula da Kula da Lafiya ta Malaysia ta ce an canja 269 daga wani jirgin ruwa mafi girma wanda ake tsammanin mutane da yawa sun mutu kuma an jefa gawarwakinsu cikin teku.
Firayim Minista Muhyiddin Yassin ya ce Malaysia ba za ta iya karbar karin 'yan gudun hijirar Rohingya ba yayin da take fama da koma bayan tattalin arziki saboda annobar coronavirus.
Amma ya ce ba za a mayar da wadanda suka riga sun shiga kasar ba zuwa teku.
Malaysia gida ce ga 'yan gudun hijira da ba a yarda da su ba fiye da miliyan biyu da kuma 'yan gudun hijira da masu neman mafaka 180,000 - ciki har da 101,000 'yan Rohingya - waɗanda aka yi wa rajista a ofishin 'yan gudun hijirar Majalisar Ɗinkin Duniya.
Amurka na kokarin kulla alaka tsakanin Isra'ila da Hadaddiyar Daular Larabawa - Leadership Hausa Newspapers
Gwamnatin Shugaba Trump za ta tura manyan jami'ai biyu zuwa Gabas ta Tsakiya a wannan makon, da nufin karfafa yarjejeniyar tarihi tsakanin Isra'ila da Hadaddiyar Daular Larabawa, don kulla dangantakar diflomasiyya.
Jami'an diflomasiyya uku sun ce Sakataren Harkokin Wajen Amurka Mike Pompeo tare da surukin Shugaba Donald Trump kuma babban mai ba da shawara, Jared Kushner, suna shirin ziyartar lokuta daban-daban da ƙasashe daban-daban a yankin a cikin 'yan kwanaki masu zuwa, don ƙarfafa sake kulla dangantaka tsakanin Daular da Isra'ila.
Ana sa ran Pompeo zai tashi a ranar Lahadi zuwa Isra'ila, Bahrain, Oman, Hadaddiyar Daular Larabawa, Qatar da Sudan, a cewar jami'an diflomasiyya da suka nemi a sakaya sunansu saboda ba a kammala ko sanar da jadawalin tafiyar ba.
Kushner, a halin yanzu, zai tashi a karshen wannan makon zuwa Isra'ila, Bahrain, Oman, Saudi Arabia da Maroko.
Ana sa ran ziyarar tasu za ta kai ga sanarwar cimma matsaya a cewar jami'an diflomasiyya, duk da cewa dukkansu suna da akalla manufa daya, ta sasanta sharuddan yarjejeniyar da Isra'ila a nan gaba kadan.
Pompeo kuma an shirya zai tattauna da kungiyar Taliban a Qatar kan batutuwan da suka shafi tattaunawar zaman lafiya, wanda zai zama muhimmin mataki wajen janye sauran sojojin Amurka daga Afghanistan.
Fadar White House da Ma'aikatar Harkokin Waje ba su yi tsokaci ba game da ziyarar da ba za ta kasance wani ɓangare na ƙoƙarin gwamnatin Amurka ba don ƙarfafa alaƙar da ke tsakanin Hadaddiyar Daular Larabawa da Isra'ila, duk da cewa ba ta cimma sulhu a cikin gwagwarmayar tsakanin Isra'ila da Falasdinawa ba.
