Hukumar NEMA ta bayar da agajin gaggawa ga wadanda ambaliyar ta shafa a Katsina.
Hukumar kula da gaggawa ta kasa (NEMA) ta ba da kayan agaji ga mutane 880 da ambaliyar ta shafa a karamar hukumar Baure da ke jihar Katsina.
Mai kula da Arewa maso Yammacin NEMA, Alhaji Abbani Imam, ya yi wannan bayani ne yayin da yake raba kayan ga masu amfana a ranar Laraba a Baure, hedkwatar karamar hukumar.
Imam ya ce kayan sun hada da 880 10kg-bags na masara, 880 10kg-bags na wake, 880 manyan filastik bags na tumatir, 880 10kg-bags na shinkafa, 880 sauro nets, 880 gerry gwangwani na man abinci da kuma wani akwati na sabulu.
Sauran kayayyaki sun hada da jakunkunan siminti, rufin rufi, itace, kusoshi, tufafi da bargo.
An samu kayan tallafin ne ta hanyar kokarin Alhaji Nasir Sani, dan majalisa na Baure / Zango a majalisar wakilai ta tarayya don rage wa mutane wahala.
"Mun zo nan don rarraba abinci da kayan abinci ba tare da fatan wannan karimci zai kawo taimako ga mutanen da abin ya shafa ba", in ji shi.
A jawabinsa, Sani ya yaba wa NEMA saboda wannan karimci.
"Dole ne in mika ta'aziyata da tausayawa ga mutanen Baure wadanda gidajensu da gonakin su suka lalace sakamakon ambaliyar", in ji shi.
Sani ya tabbatar wa jama'ar mazabarsa da karin fa'idodin dimokiradiyya.
