Hadarin ya faru ne da yammacin Asabar lokacin da jirgin Piper PA-32 mai dauke da mutane shida ya yi hatsari a wani gida a birnin Yammacin Jordan, in ji kakakin Hukumar Kula da Jiragen Sama ta Tarayya Allen Kenitzer.
