Wata mata mai shekaru 72 da ke cikin gidan da jirgin ya buge tana cikin mawuyacin hali, a cewar wani tweet ranar Lahadi daga sashen 'yan sanda.
Har ila yau, hadarin ya lalata gidaje uku, in ji mai magana da yawun birnin West Jordan Tauni Barker.
Ba a tantance musabbabin hadarin ba.
