Yadda Aka Soma Hajji a Wannan Shekarar
Yawan mutanen da za su iya halartar aikin Hajji na wannan shekara an rage su saboda yaduwar cutar coronavirus a duniya.
Maimakon masu aikin hajji sama da miliyan 2 da ke yin aikin hajji na shekara-shekara daga ko'ina cikin duniya, hukumomin kasar sun iyakance aikin hajji na wannan shekara ga 'yan kasar Saudiyya da' yan kasashen waje 1,000 da ke zaune a kasar, mutanen da aka tantance a cikin makonnin da suka gabata.
An gwada mahajjata masu shekaru tsakanin 20 zuwa 50 don COVID-19 kafin shiga Makka, inda ake buƙatar su keɓe kansu na makonni 2 a ɗakunan otal ɗin su, kafin su iya yin aikin Hajji.
Musulmai a duk faɗin duniya suna zuwa yin aikin hajji don cika ɗaya daga cikin ginshiƙan Islama, wanda shine cewa ana buƙatar mutum ya yi aikin hajji aƙalla sau ɗaya a rayuwarsa zuwa wannan wuri mafi tsarki ga mabiyan Islama.
Bayan waɗanda suka tafi aikin hajji a wannan shekara sun kammala aikin hajji, an buƙaci su ware kansu na mako guda don tabbatar da cewa ba su kamu da cutar ba yayin aikin hajji.
Sachin Pilot Vs Ashok Gehlot; BJP ta ce jihar na cikin rikicin siyasa; Majalisa na son gwajin bene
Ashok Gehlot ya ce idan ya zama dole, jam'iyyar Congress za ta gudanar da zaman gwagwarmaya a waje da gidan Firaministan.
Bayan kwana daya da jagorantar wani taro a Raj Bhawan a Jaipur, Babban Ministan jihar Rajasthan Ashok Gehlot a ranar Asabar ya ce idan ya zama dole, 'yan majalisar dokokin jam'iyyar Congress za su gana da shugaban kasa kuma su gudanar da zaman gwagwarmaya a wajen fadar firaministan don warware rikicin da ke jihar.
A wani taron jam'iyyar majalisa ta Congress (CLP), Mista Gehlot ya nuna cewa shirin shi ne a yi gwajin bene don tabbatar da cewa yawancin 'yan majalisar dokokin Congress da abokan tarayya suna tare da shi a cikin gwagwarmayar mulki.
"Ya ce gwamnati tana da rinjaye kuma tana son zuwa majalisa", in ji wata sanarwa da babban jami'in jam'iyyar Congress Mahesh Joshi ya fitar bayan taron CLP.
An gudanar da taron CLP a otal din da 'yan majalisar dokokin da ke sansanin Gehlot suka yi kwana a ciki.
"Babban ministan ya ce mu kasance a shirye mu ci gaba da zama a otal.
Idan an buƙata, in ji shi, za mu je mu sadu da Shugaban ƙasa kuma za mu gudanar da dharna a waje da gidan firaministan, "in ji wani shugaban jam'iyyar.
Gwamnan Rajasthan dole ne ya kira zaman majalisa don barin jam'iyyar Congress ta tabbatar da rinjayenta, shugaban jam'iyyar Rahul Gandhi ya ce a ranar Juma'a, yana zargin cewa shirin BJP na kifar da gwamnatin Ashok Gehlot yanzu ya bayyana.
"Ana mulkin kasar ne bisa doka da kundin tsarin mulki.
Gwamnatoci suna kafawa kuma suna gudana bisa ga umarnin mutane.
Shirye shiryen BJP na kifar da gwamnatin Rajasthan a bayyane yake.
Wannan cin mutuncin mutane miliyan 8 ne na Rajasthan.
Gwamnan dole ne ya kira zaman majalisa don gaskiyar ta zo gaban kasar, "in ji Mr Gandhi a cikin Hindi.
Babban Ministan jihar Rajasthan Ashok Gehlot ya shaida wa 'yan majalisar dokokin kasar a ranar Asabar cewa a shirye yake ya je wurin shugaban kasar India domin tabbatar da cewa abin da ya kira "shiryen BJP" don dakatar da gwajin karfi bai yi nasara ba.
Mista Gehlot, wanda ya yi zanga-zanga na tsawon awanni a gidan Gwamna Kalraj Mishra a ranar Juma'a don matsa lamba don zaman majalisar, ya yi taro da 'yan majalisar dokokin Congress da majalisar sa a ranar Asabar, bayan haka aka tsara sabon tsari kuma majalisar ta amince da shi.
Mr Mishra ya nemi Mr Gehlot ya sake gabatar da bukatar zaman majalisar, inda ya yi ikirarin cewa akwai wasu abubuwa shida da suka saɓa.
Za a aika wannan shawara ga Gwamnan nan ba da jimawa ba.
Mista Gehlot ya zargi Gwamnan da jinkirta zaman saboda yana "karkashin matsin lamba" don dakatar da gwajin ƙarfin gwamnatinsa.
Yayin da Mista Gehlot ya gana da majalisar ministocinsa, wata tawaga ta BJP karkashin jagorancin shugaban BJP na Rajasthan Satish Poonia da shugaban 'yan adawa Gulab Chandra Kataria sun gana da Gwamnan don tattauna halin da ake ciki na COVID-19 a jihar.
Kasar Sin ta dauki bakuncin CIIE wata alama ce ta burinta na raba damarta da duniya.
Shugaban kasar Sin Xi Jinping ya ce karbar bakuncin baje kolin kayayyakin da ake shigowa da su kasar Sin karo na 3 (CIIE) wata alama ce ta kudurin kasar Sin na raba damar kasuwar ta da sauran kasashen duniya, da kuma bayar da gudummawa ga farfado da tattalin arzikin duniya.
Xi, wanda ya gabatar da jawabi a bude baje kolin na wannan shekara, wanda aka bude a daren Laraba ta hanyar bidiyo, ya ce yana da muhimmanci a dage kan ka'idar ciyar da harkokin kasa da kasa gaba ta hanyar tattaunawa, da kuma kiyaye tsarin kasuwanci na bangarori da dama a karkashin jagorancin kungiyar kasuwanci ta duniya, don kara gina tattalin arzikin kasuwanci na duniya ba tare da rufewa ba.
Xi ya ci gaba da cewa, Sin ta gabatar da manufar fadada hulda tsakanin kasuwannin cikin gida, da kuma fadada hulda tsakanin kasuwannin duniya, domin biyan bukatun cikin gida, da kuma bukatun kasashen duniya.
Xi ya kara da cewa kasar Sin tana da yawan jama'a biliyan 1.4, wanda yawan mutanen da ke samun kudin shiga na kimanin yuan 5,000 na kasar Sin a kowane wata ya kai miliyan 400, wanda ya sanya kasar Sin ta zama babbar kasuwar duniya, kuma har ma an yi hasashen cewa a cikin shekaru goma masu zuwa, jimlar shigo da kayayyaki a kasar za ta kai dala tiriliyan 22.
Shugaban kasar Sin Xi Jinping ya sanar da sabbin matakai da kasarsa za ta dauka wajen bude kofa a dukkan fannoni.
Shugaban ya yi wadannan kalaman ne a jawabinsa a bikin bude bikin baje kolin kayayyakin da ake shigowa da su na kasar Sin karo na uku a birnin Shanghai.
Shugaban ya ce kasarsa za ta gabatar da jerin kayayyaki da za ta dakatar a fannin ayyukan kasuwanci na kasa da kasa, kuma za ta fadada wasu fannoni, kamar ci gaban tattalin arziki ta hanyar amfani da fasahar yanar gizo ta zamani, da zurfafa canji, kirkire-kirkire a kasuwanci da saka jari, cinikayya kyauta, da samar da yanayin kasuwanci mai kyau.
Bugu da kari, a cewar Shugaba Xi Jinping, kasar Sin za ta rage yawan fasahohin da aka haramta ko aka takaita su a matsayin shigo da su, don samar da yanayi mai kyau don musayar fasahar zamani tsakanin kasashe.
Bugu da kari, Sin za ta ci gaba da inganta tsarin shari'arta, ta yadda za ta kasance daidai da ka'idojin kasa da kasa dangane da budewa, nuna gaskiya, da karfafa kare hakkin mallakar ilimi, da kuma kare muradun masu zuba jari na kasashen waje da kuma samar musu da kariya ta shari'a.
Ya ce kasar Sin a shirye take ta rattaba hannu kan yarjejeniyar cinikayya ta kyauta don ci gaba da sauran kasashen duniya.
An Fadada Gwajin COVID-19 A Senegal
Senegal na fadada gwajin cutar coronavirus don baiwa matafiya damar yin gwaji kafin barin kasar, da kuma wadanda suka isa kasar ta Afirka ta Yamma, a cewar Reuters.
Senegal, wacce tattalin arzikinta ya dogara da yawon bude ido don samar da kusan kashi 4 na kudaden shiga daga kayayyaki da aiyukan kasar a kowace shekara, ya ce mutane 9,422 sun kamu da COVID-19 tun barkewar cutar kuma mutane 182 sun mutu.
Kusan mutane miliyan 1.7 sun tafi hutu a Senegal a shekarar 2019.
Kasar ta dage haramcin zirga-zirgar jiragen sama na kasa da kasa daga ranar 15 ga watan Yuli amma ta ce za ta hana wadanda suka hana 'yan kasar Senegal shiga kasashensu.
Ma'aikatar Lafiya ta kafa cibiyoyin gwaji na COVID-19 4 a babban birnin Dakar don gwada matafiya, daga cikinsu a lokacin barkewar cutar akwai guda ɗaya kawai.
