Babbar kotun jihar Kano ta dage sauraron karar da dan takarar gwamnan jihar Kano Abba Kabir Yusuf ya shigar wanda ke kalubalantar sayar da wasu kadarorin gwamnati da gwamnan jihar Kano Abdullaji Umar Ganduje ya yi.
Wakilin Nadabo Isam'il Yusuf ya ruwaito cewa a yayin zaman na yau, Alkali Nura Sagir ya dage shari'ar zuwa ranar 29 ga Oktoba na wannan shekarar.
Lauyan Abba Kabir Yusuf, Bashir Yusuf Tudun Wuzirici, ya ce shawarar da gwamnan jihar Kano ya yanke na sayar da kadarorin gwamnati ta sabawa dokar kula da filayen jihar Kano.
Barista Musa Abdullahi Lawal, lauya ga kwamishinan shari'a na jihar, ya ce korafin ba shi da tushe kuma ba zai yiwu ba.
