Jami'in FDNY ya ce 'hakika' yana da kyau don cire fararen wuta daga tsaro mai launi
Wani jami'in bambancin FDNY ya ce 'da gaske' abin yarda ne a kiyaye fararen 'yan wuta daga tsaron launi na bikin don masu tutar su kasance baki, a cewar wani sabon rahoto.
Fitaccen dan wuta Laftanar Daniel McWilliams ya shigar da kara yana ikirarin nuna bambancin launin fata bayan an cire shi daga wani rukunin da ke dauke da tutar a watan Nuwamba 2017 taron tunawa da membobin da suka mutu na kungiyar Vulcan, wata kungiya ta 'yan uwantaka ta bakaken fata.
Kuma babban jami'in bambancin da hada kan FDNY, lauya Cecilia Loving, ya kare hukuncin a wata shari'ar da aka yi a New York ta sashen kare hakkin bil adama, The New York Post ta ruwaito.
McWilliams na daya daga cikin 'yan wuta uku na FDNY da aka gani a cikin hoto mai ban mamaki yayin da suke ɗaga tutar Amurka a Ground Zero a cikin kwanaki bayan hare-haren 9/11.
A cewar McWilliams, an zabe shi ne daga sashen kula da bikin FDNY don ya zama daya daga cikin masu dauke da tutar a cikin masu tsaron launi a bikin tunawa.
Kasancewa mai dauke da tutar a taron 'girma ne da gata' ga McWilliams, a cewar karar da ya shigar, CNN ta ruwaito.
Bayan isowarsa taron, duk da haka, an hana McWilliams shiga cikin mai tsaron launi ta shugaban kungiyar Vulcan Regina Wilson saboda an ce ta nemi mai tsaron launi baki a taron.
Sai ta nemi McWilliams - tsohon soja mai shekaru 29 na FDNY - ya 'taimaka a wani matsayi daban.'
Daga cikin waɗannan ayyuka, an ce ya bi da farar hula kuma ya tara jami'an da suka saka tufafi a cikin rukuni daga taron.
McWilliams ya yi ikirarin a cikin karar da ya yi cewa ya tambayi Wilson idan ta cire shi daga mai kare launi saboda ba baƙar fata ba ne.
Ta tabbatar da cewa haka lamarin yake, in ji shi.
Wilson, tsohon soja ne na shekaru 21 wanda kuma ya kasance wani ɓangare na ƙoƙarin ceto na 9/11, a bayyane yake ya maye gurbin McWilliams da ɗaya daga cikin mambobi na kungiyar Vulcan.
McWilliams ya yi ikirarin cewa ya bar abin tunawa 'don ya ceci kansa daga ƙarin kunya, wulakanci da kunya,' kamar yadda abokai da abokan aiki suka ji tattaunawarsu, jaridar New York Daily News ta ruwaito.
A lokacin da take ba da shaida a kotu, lauyan McWilliams, Keith Sullivan, ya tambayi Loving - wadda baƙar fata ce - 'To, roƙon da aka yi na a yi wa baƙar fata duka tsaro ba nuna bambanci ba ne?'
'A'a, ba haka ba ne,' in ji Loving, in ji jaridar New York Post.
Sullivan kuma ya tambayi Loving idan yana da kyau a nemi mai kare launi baki baki, wanda aka nakalto ta ce, 'Tabbas tabbas.'
A matsayin bayani, Loving ya ce yana da kyau a musanya fararen fata da baƙar fata don 'haɓaka asalinmu da kabilunmu daban-daban don sanya girman kai da al'umma da tallafawa juna.'
McWilliams ya fara shigar da korafin nuna bambancin launin fata tare da FDNY a watan Janairun 2018.
Daga nan sai ya shigar da kara a kan Wilson, FDNY, birnin New York da kuma wasu mutane da ba a bayyana sunayensu ba a watan Mayu 2019.
Bayan ya shigar da korafinsa, Sullivan ya ce magoya bayan Wilson sun yi wa McWilliams azaba kuma sun tsoratar da shi.
A wani lokaci, an ce ɗaya cikin magoya bayanta ya ɗora wa McWilliams hannu ya ce: 'Na ji labarinka, sun gaya mini cewa za ka yi haka, kuma yanzu ka san ni.'
A cikin taƙaitaccen bayani, Sullivan ya rubuta cewa ƙin McWilliams daga matsayin mai tsaron launi na taro 'abin kunya ne' kuma alamar ma'auni biyu a sashen kashe gobara.
'Idan kai baƙar fata ne kuma kana nuna bambanci ga wani farar fata a wurin aiki, za ka sami bulala a wuyan hannu,' in ji Sullivan.
Wilson, a cewar karar, ta samu 'sa'a daya na ba da shawara' game da yadda ta bi da McWilliams.
A wani ɓangare kuma, wani farar fata da ya nuna bambanci ga wani baƙar fata yana samun 'matsanancin horo da kuma horo,' in ji Sullivan.
'FDNY ta kirkiro manufofi da hanyoyin da za su yi baya, su fito da uzuri da kuma karbar bakuncin mambobin kungiyar Vulcan ... wadanda ke aikata ayyukan wariyar launin fata, kuma dole ne a daina, 'Sullivan ya kuma rubuta.
Noma ya bunkasa tattalin arzikin Najeriya, duk da matsalolin tattalin arziki.
Bangaren noma a Najeriya ya ba da gudummawa ga ci gaban tattalin arziki da kashi 24.6 cikin dari a watan Afrilu, Mayu zuwa Yuni, fiye da watannin Janairu, Fabrairu da Maris, da Afrilu, Mayu da Yuni 2019.
Ofishin kididdiga na kasa ya bayyana hakan a wani rahoto da aka fitar a ranar Litinin.
Rahoton da hukumar ta fitar a ranar Litinin, ya nuna cewa karfin tattalin arzikin Najeriya ya ragu sosai a watan Afrilu, Mayu da Yuni 2020.
Ƙarfin Gross Domestic Product (GDP) shine ma'auni na cinikayya a cikin kayayyakin da aka samar a cikin ƙasa a cikin ƙasa da kuma kudaden kuɗi a cikin ƙasa.
Bangaren aikin gona ya ba da gudummawar kashi 24.65 cikin dari a watan Afrilu, Mayu da Yuni 2020, fiye da waɗannan watanni uku a shekarar 2019, lokacin da ya kai kashi 22.78 cikin dari.
Kuma fiye da watan Janairu, Fabrairu da Maris, 2020, wanda ya kai kashi 22.96 cikin dari.
Wannan ya nuna cewa adadin ya ƙaru da kashi 19.90 a wannan lokacin na bara.
Wato, idan muka yi la'akari da hauhawar farashin kayayyaki da kuma tsadar kayayyaki, za mu ga cewa bangaren noma ya ba da gudummawar kashi 23.9 cikin dari na GDP na Najeriya.
Wato, aikin gona ya bunkasa tattalin arzikin kasar da kashi 1.58 cikin dari na jimlar tattalin arzikin kasa, daga shekarar 2019 zuwa 2020.
Rahoton ya ce bangaren noma da kansa ya karu da kashi 6.57 cikin dari idan aka kwatanta da ci gabansa a watan Janairu zuwa Maris a farkon 2020.
Bangaren noma a Najeriya ya kunshi bangarori hudu da suka hada da samar da abinci, kiwo, bunkasa gandun daji da kamun kifi.
