Yanayin Gareth Bale a Real Madrid 'ba ya gamsar da kowa,' in ji Toni Kroos
Dan wasan tsakiya na Real Madrid Toni Kroos ya ce halin da Gareth Bale ke ciki a kungiyar ta Spain "ba ya gamsar da kowa".
Bale bai buga wasa a cikin wasanni bakwai da suka gabata ba kuma ya kasance wani mutum ne a cikin bikin LaLiga na Los Blancos kafin wani rikici na bazara yayin da dan wasan ke neman zama don ganin kwangilarsa da fatan kulob din zai tafi.
"Babu wata hanyar da za a guji halin da ake ciki wanda ba ya gamsar da kowa", Kroos ya fada wa Lauschangriff Endlich was mit Sport! podcast.
"Ba su sanya hannu a kan shi ba don ya yi wasa kadan kamar yadda yake yanzu.
"Ina ganin a ka'ida ya so ya tafi bara kuma kulob din ya ce 'eh' a ka'ida sannan kuma 'a'a' bayan haka.
"Ban san ko har yanzu yana fushi saboda hakan ba.
Da aka tambaye shi ko halin da ake ciki ya yi mummunan tasiri a kan yanayi a Real, Kroos ya ce: "Tabbas ba kamar yadda yake ba.
"Duk abin da ke cikin tawagar yana da kyau. Na san shi tsawon shekaru shida kuma mun ci wasu abubuwa masu muhimmanci tare".
Za a Bude Makarantu A Najeriya Domin Binciken WAEC
Gwamnatin Najeriya ta sanar da cewa makarantu za su sake budewa a ranar 4 ga watan Agusta ga daliban makarantar sakandare na shekarar karshe don zama don gwajin WAEC.
Gwamnati ta sanar da wannan matakin a cikin wata sanarwa da Ma'aikatar Ilimi ta fitar a ranar Litinin, wanda Daraktan yada labarai na Ma'aikatar, Ben Bem Goong ya sanya hannu.
