Gwamnatin Jihar Neja Ta Yabawa Shugabancin Sultan Yayin da Ya Kai Shekara 64.
Gwamnan jihar Neja kuma shugaban kungiyar gwamnonin Arewa da Tsakiya, Alhaji Abubakar Sani Bello, ya taya Sultan na Sokoto, Alhaji Muhammad Sa'ad Abubakar III murnar cika shekaru 64.
Sanarwar ranar haihuwar ta kasance a cikin sanarwar manema labarai da sakataren yada labarai na gwamna, Mary Noel Berje, ya sanya hannu, yana taya janar mai ritaya murna a wannan karon.
A cewar sanarwar, Gwamna Abubakar Sani Bello ya bayyana Sultan na Najeriya a matsayin dan Najeriya na gaskiya wanda yake mai gaskiya, mai gwagwarmayar hadin kai da zaman lafiya domin kasar ta ci gaba.
Gwamnan ya ce a matsayinsa na shugaban kungiyar Jama'atu Nasrul Islam (JNI) da shugaban majalisar koli ta Najeriya kan harkokin Musulunci (NSCIA), da kuma shugaban majalisar Najeriya ta addini (NIREC), ya taka muhimmiyar rawa wajen ci gaban wannan kasa.
Gwamnan ya ce a matsayinsa na shugaban kungiyar gwamnonin Arewa ta Tsakiya, wanda ke da alhakin hadin kai da ci gaban yankin da kuma Najeriya baki daya, "Zan iya bayyana cewa haihuwar mai girma Sultan a wannan yankin ba karamar jinkai ba ce a gare mu, saboda aikinsa da gaskiya wajen gudanar da shugabancin gargajiya kamar yadda ya dace ".
Alkawarin da kuka yi na zaman lafiya da hadin kai ya nuna salon shugabancin mutanen Arewa.Za mu ci gaba da farin ciki tare da ku saboda yadda kuke ba da kanku da lokacinku ga mutanen ƙasar, saboda kyawawan manufofinku a gare su game da al'adu, addini da dabarun siyasa.Kasancewar ku da burinku na inganta zaman lafiya da hadin kai ga mabiyan addinai.
A matsayinka na cikakken jagora kuma mai mulkin gargajiya, a tsawon shekaru ka horar da kanka don tabbatar da cewa akwai yanayi mai kyau ga zaman lafiya a kasar, ta hanyar sanarwar hadin gwiwa da zaman lafiya wanda ke inganta kyakkyawar fahimta tsakanin addinai da al'adu.
Ina yi muku fatan alheri da sauran 'yan Najeriya a wannan rana, kuma ina yaba muku kan yadda kuke inganta fahimtar juna tsakanin mutane masu addini a cikin kasar da wajenta da kuma kokarin da kuke yi a kasar nan.
Gwamnan ya yaba wa mai martaba Sultan saboda yaƙinsa da talauci, inganta kiwon lafiya da shirye-shirye kan ci gaban ilimi a fannin fasaha da ƙwarewa a yankin, da kuma kasancewa mai mulkin gargajiya na mutane.
Gwamnan ya yi addu'ar Allah ya baiwa Sultan lafiya mai kyau da karin shekaru na hidima mai amfani, da farin ciki da kuzari don ci gaba da tushen zaman lafiya da ci gaba a duk kasar.
Na kara masa fatan ranar haihuwa mai albarka ga mai martaba Sultan.
