Maurice Petty, mai gina injin da aka sani da gina injina, ya mutu yana da shekara 81
KANSAS CITY, Kan. (AP) - Maurice Petty, wani ɓangare na dangi na tseren motar da ya haɗa da mahaifinsa Lee da ɗan'uwansa Richard da kuma injiniyar injiniya ta farko da za a shigar da shi cikin NASCAR Hall of Fame, ya mutu ranar Asabar.
Yana da shekara 81.
Iyalin Petty ba su bayyana dalilin mutuwar ba.
Ba a sanar da yadda za a yi jana'izar ba.
Yayin da sauran 'yan gidan suka yi farin ciki da kwarewarsu a bayan motar, Maurice Petty ya sami lakabi "The Chief" don ikonsa na juya maɓallin kewayawa.
Ya taimaka wa danginsa lashe tsere 198 da zakaru bakwai a cikin manyan jerin NASCAR, kuma ya kuma gina injunan da suka kai Hall of Famer Buddy Baker, Jim Paschal da Pete Hamilton zuwa nasara.
"Shugaba yana daya daga cikin masu fasaha mafi basira a tarihin NASCAR", in ji shugaban da babban darakta Jim France.
"Ya samar da ikon da ya taimaka wa kananan kamfanoni su bayyana mamayar wasanni.
Duk da yake an san shi da aikinsa a ƙarƙashin murfin, Maurice ya taka rawar gani da yawa a bayan fage, yana yin abin da ya kamata don taimakawa wajen kawo motocinsa zuwa hanyar nasara. "
An haifi Maurice Petty a ranar 27 ga Maris, 1939, a Level Cross, North Carolina.
Zai bi mahaifinsa zuwa waƙa yayin da yake girma, kuma saninsa na injiniya ya taka muhimmiyar rawa a cikin Lee Petty lashe tseren 54 da gasar zakarun Turai uku.
Ya fara 26 a cikin NASCAR Cup Series daga 1960-64, ya gama a cikin manyan 5 sau bakwai tare da 16 saman 10 gudu.
Amma da sauri ya yanke shawarar mai da hankali kan abin da ke faruwa a ƙarƙashin kaho maimakon abin da ke faruwa a bayan motar, kuma wannan ya tabbatar da kyakkyawan motsi ga ɗan'uwansa, wanda zai dogara da injunansa a lokacin da yake rinjaye.
Richard, wanda zai dauki sunan "The King", ya lashe gasar farko tare da The Chief lokacin da ya kori Plymouth zuwa taken 1964.
Sun sake lashe gasar a 1967, sun sake lashe gasar a 1970 da '71, kuma sun kara uku kafin shekarun 1970 suka kawo karshen.
Takardun bakwai sun kasance daidai da Dale Earnhardt da Jimmie Johnson a mafi yawan tarihi.
"Maurice Petty na daya daga cikin masu ba da labari na gaskiya a NASCAR wanda ya taimaka wajen gina daya daga cikin manyan kungiyoyin NASCAR a cikin Kamfanonin Kasuwanci", in ji darektan zartarwa na Hall of Fame Winston Kelley a cikin wata sanarwa.
"Ko da yake rikodin ya nuna nasara 212, Petty yana da nasara fiye da 250 a cikin bashi idan aka la'akari da dukan injunan da ya gina ga masu fafatawa.
Shugaban za a tuna da shi har abada a matsayin daya daga cikin mafi kyawun gina tashoshin wutar lantarki a NASCAR. "
Lee Petty ya mutu a shekara ta 2000 kuma matar Maurice Petty na shekaru 52, Patricia, ta mutu a shekarar 2014.
Shi ma kawun tsohon direba ne kuma mai watsa shirye-shirye Kyle Petty da kuma shugaban ma'aikatan Truck Series Trent Owens.
"Duk da cewa mun rasa daya daga cikin manyan, masu kwazo da kuma jarumai na NASCAR, za a tuna da Maurice Petty da kuma tunawa da shi, za a kiyaye shi, a yi bikin kuma a yaba da shi", in ji Kelley.
"Muna mika ta'aziyyarmu ga iyalin Petty".
Francois Bozize, shugaban CAR da aka tsige, ya sanar da neman shugabancin kasar
Tsohon shugaban Jamhuriyar Afirka ta Tsakiya da aka sauke Francois Bozize ya sanar a ranar Asabar cewa zai tsaya takarar shugaban kasa a zaben watan Disamba duk da cewa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta sanya masa takunkumi kuma an ba shi umarnin kama shi saboda zargin aikata laifuka kan bil'adama.
Ya sanar da hakan ne a jawabin da ya gabatar ga dimbin magoya bayansa a wani taron jam'iyyarsa, Kwa na Kwa (Aiki, Babu Abinda Sai Aiki), a Bangui babban birnin kasar.
Tsohon janar kuma shugaban sojojin mai shekaru 73 da haihuwa an hambarar da shi a cikin tawaye na 2013 ta hanyar kawancen 'yan tawayen Musulmi da suka fito daga arewa, wanda ya jefa kasar da ke da rinjaye a cikin yakin basasa da rikici mai tsanani da ci gaba da rikici.
"Kasar na bukatar wani mutum mai kwarewa, zaman lafiya da kuma imani", in ji Bozize a jawabin da ya soki wa'adin shugaban kasar na yanzu, Faustin-Archange Touadera.
Bozize ya fara mulki ne bayan juyin mulki a shekarar 2003 kuma ya yi shekaru 10 a matsayin shugaban kasa kafin ya tsere daga kasar a shekarar 2013.
Sabuwar gwamnatin ta nemi a kama shi saboda zargin aikata laifuka kan bil'adama da kuma ta'addanci, amma ba ta yi wani mataki ba don kama shi tun lokacin da ya dawo daga gudun hijira a karshen shekarar da ta gabata.
Ba a san yadda umarnin ko takunkumin kasashen waje zai shafi takararsa ba.
A watan Janairu, Bozize ya ce zai nemi Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta dage takunkumin da aka sanya a shekarar 2014 saboda zarginsa na goyon bayan kungiyoyin 'yan ta'adda na Anti-balaka.
Touadera na mulki a yau tare da goyon bayan babban aikin wanzar da zaman lafiya na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya da sojoji da 'yan sanda sama da 13,000.
An zabe shi a shekarar 2016, ana sa ran zai nemi wa'adi na biyu a zaben amma har yanzu bai tabbatar da cewa zai tsaya takara ba.
An shirya zagayen farko na tseren a ranar 27 ga watan Disamba.
Gwamnati ta sanya hannu kan yarjejeniyar zaman lafiya a watan Fabrairun 2019 tare da kungiyoyi 14 masu dauke da makamai, wadanda galibi ke ikirarin kare bukatun wasu al'ummomi ko addinai.
Tun daga wannan lokacin tashin hankali ya ragu, amma har yanzu akwai wasu hare-hare masu kisa, yawanci ana haifar da su ne saboda fadace-fadace kan albarkatu kuma mafi yawan kasar mai arzikin lu'u-lu'u ta kasance ba ta ƙarƙashin ikon gwamnati.
Rikicin ya tilasta wa mutane fiye da miliyan 1.5 su bar gidajensu.
