Masu zanga-zangar nuna kyamar wariyar launin fata sun yi arangama da 'yan sanda a Seattle
Rikicin da aka yi a Seattle tsakanin 'yan sanda da masu zanga-zangar nuna kyamar wariyar launin fata ya haifar da dubun dubatan kama mutane a ranar Lahadi, yayin da fushin jama'a ke ƙaruwa kan shirin "ƙaruwar" jami'an tarayya a manyan biranen da Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya shirya.
An fara zanga-zangar nuna adawa da wariyar launin fata da zaluncin 'yan sanda sakamakon mutuwar wani Ba'amurke dan Afirka mai suna George Floyd a Minneapolis a watan Mayu.
Masu zanga-zangar a Seattle sun yanke tayoyin motoci da kuma fasa tagogin tirela yayin zanga-zangar ranar Asabar, wanda ya sa 'yan sanda suka ayyana tarzoma da share tituna da feshin barkono da kuma bama-bamai masu fashewa.
Masu zanga-zangar sun kuma banka wa tirela wuta a wani wurin da ake gina gidan yarin matasa.
'Yan sanda sun ce an kama mutane 45 yayin da jami'ai 21 suka ji rauni.
Taron ya nuna goyon baya ga zanga-zangar da ake yi a kusa da Portland, Oregon.
Portland ta zama cibiyar tattaunawa a kan rikicin da jami'an tarayya suka yi bisa umarnin Trump - wanda jami'an yankin ba su goyi bayansa ba, wadanda suka ce jami'an sun yi amfani da karfi sosai.
Masu zanga-zangar sun yi zanga-zanga a Austin, Texas, da kuma Louisville, Kentucky; New York; Omaha, Nebraska; Oakland da Los Angeles na California, da Richmond a Virginia.
A Austin, an kashe wani mutum a harbi da ya barke a daren Asabar a wani zanga-zanga a tsakiyar birnin babban birnin jihar Texas, in ji 'yan sanda.
Zanga-zangar ta zo ne yayin da Trump ke fuskantar gwagwarmaya mai tsauri don sake zaɓe a watan Nuwamba, kuma yana yin kamfen a kan tsarin "doka da tsari".
Yaƙin neman zaɓen Biden ya ƙi ganawar 'Fox News Sunday', mako guda bayan tattaunawar Trump ta Chris Wallace
A yayin ganawarsa da Chris Wallace a makon da ya gabata, Shugaba Trump ya yi tambaya ko dan takarar shugaban kasa na jam'iyyar Democrat, Joe Biden, zai iya magance matsalar da Wallace ya gabatar wa Trump.
Wataƙila ba za mu taɓa sanin amsar wannan tambayar ba.
Wallace a ranar Lahadi ya sanar da masu kallo cewa yakin neman zaben Biden ya gaya wa Fox News cewa "ba shi da damar" don hira.
"A hirarmu da muka yi da Shugaba Trump a makon da ya gabata, ya yi tambaya ko abokin hamayyarsa na jam'iyyar Democrat, Joe Biden, zai iya fuskantar irin wannan lamarin", in ji Wallace.
"A wannan makon, mun nemi kamfen din Biden don ganawa kuma sun ce tsohon mataimakin shugaban ba ya nan".
Ya daɗa cewa, "Za mu ci gaba da yin hakan kowane mako".
Gangamin Trump ya buge Biden tsawon watanni saboda ya guji yin gangami da taron manema labarai yayin ci gaba da yin tambayoyi a cikin annobar coronavirus.
Yayin da Biden ya dawo kwanan nan, Trump da kawayensa sun ci gaba da ba'a tsohon mataimakin shugaban don "ɓoye" a gidansa a Delaware.
Rashin son yin taron jama'a na Biden, duk da haka, bai yi tasiri sosai ga takarar sa ba kamar yadda binciken da aka yi kwanan nan ya sa Biden ya fi Trump gaba a ƙasa da kuma manyan jihohin da ake faɗa.
Matsakaicin siyasa na gaskiya ya nuna cewa shugaban ya fadi da maki 7 a Florida, maki 6.7 a Pennsylvania, maki 8.2 a Michigan da maki 6.4 a Wisconsin.
Trump ya samu nasara a jihohi hudu a 2016, ya juya su daga shuɗi zuwa ja yayin da ya lashe fadar White House.
Binciken Fox News na baya-bayan nan ya sanya Biden a gaba a Minnesota, Michigan da Pennsylvania, tare da jagororin da ke waje da kuskuren kuskure.
Binciken ya kuma nuna Biden yana da ɗan fa'ida a Ohio, North Carolina da Arizona, wasu manyan jihohi uku masu canji a wannan zagaye.
Kuma, binciken ya nuna cewa jihohin da aka taɓa amincewa da su kamar Texas da Georgia duk sun haɗu tsakanin Trump da tsohon mataimakin shugaban.
Zaben shugaban kasa wanda wani mai mulki ke neman wa'adi na biyu a fadar White House galibi kuri'ar raba gardama ce kan wannan shugaban - kuma ana ganin hakan a halin yanzu a cikin gwagwarmayar 2020 tsakanin Trump da Biden.
Manyan batutuwan sune coronavirus da tattalin arziki da annobar ta lalata - da kuma aikin shugaban da rikodin a kan batutuwan biyu.
