Laura da Sam sun fara haduwa a shekarar 2011 a wani gwaji kuma Sam, wanda kuma ya kasance a cikin Peaky Blinders, ya bayyana aurensu a shekarar 2013 a matsayin "mai sauƙin daya daga cikin manyan nasarorin da ya samu".
Kafin White Lines, Laura ta bayyana a fim din farko na Inbetweeners da kuma wasan kwaikwayo na BBC na bara The Capture, inda ta taka rawar lauya Hannah Roberts.
Tom ya bayyana a cikin Inbetweeners sequel da Sky drama Britannia.
Harin da aka kai kan kafafen yada labarai na Najeriya na da matukar damuwa - Majalisar Dinkin Duniya.
