Virginia Roberts, wacce ake zargi da zama bawan jima'i na wani mai kudi na Amurka, ta yi ikirarin a cikin takardun kotu na 2015 cewa an tilasta mata yin jima'i da Yarima Andrew
Yarima Andrew yana shirin yaki da yiwuwar bayyana wannan makon na kara zarge-zarge game da abokantakarsa da mai lalata yara Jeffrey Epstein da kuma wanda ake zargi da laifin Ghislaine Maxwell.
Alkalin kotun Amurka Loretta Preska a makon da ya gabata ta bayar da umarnin sakin takardu 80 na sirri, wanda ya kai daruruwan shafuka, da suka shafi Maxwell da Epstein.
Bayyana wannan babban adadin takardu zai zama babban rauni ga Maxwell, mai shekaru 58, saboda suna dauke da manyan sassan shaidar da ta bayar ga lauyoyi a shekarar 2016, gami da abin da ƙungiyar lauyoyinta ta ce "tambaya ce mai saurin shiga" game da rayuwarta ta jima'i.
Hakanan zasu iya matsa lamba ga Yarima Andrew saboda ɗayan takaddun sun haɗa da sadarwa tsakanin Maxwell da Epstein daga Janairu 2015, lokacin da Virginia Roberts, wanda ake zargi da bautar jima'i ta mai ba da kuɗin Amurka mai kunya, ta yi iƙirarin a cikin takardun kotu cewa an tilasta mata yin jima'i da Yarima a lokuta uku.
Andrew ya yi ta musanta wannan ikirarin.
Wani sakon imel da aka fallasa daga shekarar 2015 wanda BBC ta bayyana a bara ya nuna cewa Andrew ya nemi taimakon Maxwell wajen magance zargin Ms Roberts.
Ba mu da wata shakka cewa Duke zai sami 'yancinsa.
A cikinta, ya gaya wa mai shahararren: "Ka sanar da ni lokacin da za mu iya magana. Ina da wasu tambayoyi na musamman da zan yi maka game da Virginia Roberts".
Maxwell ya ce: "Ka ba ni wasu bayanai, ka kira ni idan ka samu lokaci".
A daren jiya, wata majiya da ke kusa da Andrew ta ce: "Duke na York bai yi wani laifi ba, don haka muna da kwanciyar hankali game da buɗe duk wani takardun kotu.
Kamar yadda kotunan Amurka suka yi ƙoƙari su nuna, kawai saboda an haɗa da zargi a cikin takardun kotu ba ya sa su zama gaskiya.
"Kotunan Amurka sun bukaci kafofin yada labarai da jama'a da su kula da duk wani zargi da ke cikin takardun kotu da taka tsantsan.
Mun yarda gaba ɗaya.
Ba mu da wata shakka cewa Duke zai sami cikakken tabbaci a cikin makonni masu zuwa. "
Maxwell yana tsare a Manhattan Metropolitan Detention Center yana jiran shari'a don daukar ma'aikata da kuma kula da wasu daga cikin wadanda Epstein ya kashe tsakanin 1994 da 1997.
An kuma zarge ta da yin rantsuwa saboda kin amincewa da ilimin da ta samu a shari'a game da cin zarafinsa.
Ta musanta duk zargin.
Lauyoyi sun yi hira da Maxwell a watan Afrilu da Yuli na 2016 a matsayin wani ɓangare na karar da Ms Roberts ta gabatar, wanda yanzu ya yi amfani da sunan mahaifiyarta Giuffre.
Kimanin shafuka 40 daga cikin shaidu 418 da aka bayyana a bara, amma bayan hukuncin da Alkali Preska ya yanke a makon da ya gabata a New York, za a iya buɗe wasu sassan a ranar Alhamis.
An bai wa lauyoyin Maxwell mako guda su yi roko.
An gano Epstein ya mutu a gidan yarin New York a shekarar da ta gabata yayin da yake jiran shari'a kan laifin lalata.
MOPPAN ta sake jaddada fitar da Rahama Sadau.
Hukumar tace fina-finan Kano ce ta dawo da ita, a cewar masu shirya fim din.
Kungiyar masu sana'ar fim ta Kannywood da aka fi sani da MOPPAN ta sake jaddada shawarar da ta yanke na korar daya daga cikin fitattun jarumai a masana'antar fina-finan Hausa, Rahama Sadau bayan da wani ya zagi Manzon Allah (SAW) sakamakon zargin da tauraruwar fim din ta yi na wallafa duk hotunan ta a yayin da yake tsokaci.
Za a tuna cewa, Jaruma Rahama Sadau ta fuskanci suka da cin mutunci daga al'ummomin Musulmi da Hausa da kuma abokan aikinta da yawa saboda sanya hoton ta da tsirara a shafin Twitter, wani aiki da ya haifar da cece-kuce tsakanin mabiya addinai daban-daban, bayan da wani mai sharhi, wanda ake zargin ba musulmi ba ne, ya zagi Annabi Allah.
Wannan ya haifar da laƙabin "Mataimakin Allah", kalmomin da ake zargin actress ta fara amfani da su a ƙoƙarin nuna rashin jin daɗin ta game da abubuwan da ta sha wahala daga wasu game da hoton, daga waɗanda suka ce wannan ya sabawa koyarwar Islama, wanda ta bi.
Bayan wanda ake zargin ya yi ba'a game da Annabi ya kuma yi suka, wannan ya jawo suka har ma daga masu yin fina-finai a Arewacin Najeriya, don haka wannan ƙungiyar masu yin fina-finai ta fito ta nisanta kanta da jarumar.
A wata sanarwa da shugaban kasa, Dakta Ahmad Sarari ya fitar a jiya, jami'in hulda da jama'a na kungiyar, Al-Amin Ciroma ya yi Allah wadai da ayyukan Rahama, yana mai cewa jaruma ce da ta bata a kungiyar, sai dai hukumar tantance fina-finan jihar Kano (KSCB) karkashin jagorancin Ismail Na'abba Afakallahu ba zato ba tsammani ta dawo da ita.
Kungiyar ta tuna cewa tun daga shekarar 2016, an kori jarumar daga masana'antar saboda keta dokar kungiyar bayan ta fito a wani bidiyo tare da wani mawaƙa mai suna Classic wanda suke rungumar juna.
Sanarwar ta ci gaba da cewa, "Kungiyar da ke kula da dukkan 'yan wasan kwaikwayo a kungiyar masana'antar fim ta Arewacin Najeriya, MOPPAN, wanda kuma aka fi sani da Kannywood, ta nuna rashin jin dadinta game da sanya hoton fitacciyar jarumar Rahama Sadau a shafukan sada zumunta", hoton da ke yaduwa a kafafen yada labarai.
Hoton ya jawo suka da yawa, kamar yadda hoton ya haifar da cin mutuncin Annabi Muhammad (SAW) a Twitter da sauran dandamali na kafofin sada zumunta.
Wannan laifi ne mai ban tsoro kuma MOPPAN ta la'anci hakan.
Idan za a iya tunawa, kimanin shekaru hudu da suka gabata, a ranar 2 ga Oktoba, 2016, kungiyar ta kori Sadau daga masana'antar fim, amma bayan kimanin shekaru biyu KSCB ta ce ta yafe mata, duk da cewa Kano ita ce babbar cibiyar samar da fina-finan Hausa a duniya.
MOPPAN ta ce, "Shekaru biyu bayan korar, Hukumar Kula da Fim ta Jihar Kano (KSCB) ta hannun shugabanta, Mallam Isma'il Na'Abba Afakkallah".
A ranar 8 ga Janairun 2018, kungiyar ta yafe wa Rahama duk wani laifin da ake zargin ta yi, kuma ta ba ta damar sake shiga Kannywood, matakin da reshen MOPPAN na jihar Kano ya kalubalanci a ranar 15 ga Janairun 2018, a karkashin jagorancin shugaban reshen, Malam Kabiru Maikaba.
Sanarwar ta kara da cewa, "Ganin halin da ake ciki yanzu, MOPPAN ta sake tabbatar da matsayinta na farko kan Rahama Sadau kuma ta yi kira ga dukkan kungiyoyin Kannywood da su bi wannan shawarar kuma su aiwatar da ita".
Daga nan MOPPAN ta yi kira ga dukkan kwararru a Kannywood da sauran al'ummar Hausa a gida da waje da su lura da cewa kungiyar ta riga ta nisanta kanta da Rahama Sadau da duk wani laifi da za ta iya yi yanzu ko a nan gaba.
Mutane sun sake jin zafi cewa tauraron fim din ya ki cire post dinta da hotunanta na kwanaki.
To, amma kuma bayan abubuwa sun kara tsanantawa, tauraron fim din ya cire hotunan kuma a jiya da yamma ta fito a shafukan sada zumunta tare da rubutu da bidiyo tana nisantar kanta daga sharhin cin mutunci game da Annabi (SAW) da kuma mutumin da ya yi shi, kodayake Sadau bai fito fili ya amsa cewa ba daidai ba ne a saka hotunan a farkon wuri.
