Harbin ya faru ne kafin karfe 10 na dare a yayin zanga-zangar a Austin, kakakin 'yan sanda Katrina Ratliff ya fadawa manema labarai da sanyin safiyar Lahadi.
An kai mutumin asibiti inda daga baya aka bayyana mutuwarsa.
Motar ta busa ƙaho, ta juya ta hanyar sannan ta hanzarta zuwa masu zanga-zangar, shaidar Michael Capochiano ta gaya wa Austin American-Statesman.
Mutumin, wanda Capochiano ya ce yana dauke da bindiga, ya kusanci motar kuma direba ya harbe shi.
Sai direban ya tafi, in ji Capochiano.
Rahotanni na farko sun nuna "mai yiwuwa wanda aka kashe yana dauke da bindiga", in ji Ratliff ga manema labarai, yana mai cewa an tsare wanda ake zargin kuma yana aiki tare da 'yan sanda.
