Mataimakin Gwamna AbdulRahman AbdulRazaq, Kayode Oyin-Zubair, ya sanar da ci gaban al'umma a Ilorin a ranar Talata.
Oyin-Zubair ya ce za a bai wa kowace mace naira 10,000 a karshen shekarar 2020.
Ya ce gwamnati tana yin hakan ne don inganta yanayin rayuwar mutanen karkara don rage cunkoson ababen hawa a birane, don haka wadanda ke kauyuka su ma su iya shiga kasuwanci maimakon zuwa birane.
Sannan gwamnati za ta yi aiki tare da hukumar "Forestry Research Institute of Nigeria (FRIN) " don samar wa mata da tsaba na sauro don su ci gaba da gasa a aikin gona.
Ya ce gwamnati za ta shirya tare da gwamnatin Kenya don cinikin tsaba na kwaɗi a kasuwannin wannan ƙasar da kuma wasu ƙasashe.
A ranar 28 ga watan Oktoba, PREMIUM TIMES ta ruwaito cewa Gwamnatin Tarayya ta samar da tallafin N20,000 ga kowane mata 2,800 na karkara a jihar Zamfara ta hanyar Shirin Ba da Tallafi ga Mata na Karkara.
Ministan jin kai, agaji da ci gaban rayuwa, Hajiya Sadiya Umar Farouq, ita ma ta yi wannan sanarwar, tana mai cewa wannan tallafin na daga cikin kokarin Shugaba Muhammadu Buhari na cika alkawarin gwamnatinsa na magance matsalar jama'a.
