Za a fara tsagaita wuta a gabashin Ukraine da aka yi yaki da shi da tsakar dare
KYIV, Ukraine -- Sojojin Ukraine da 'yan tawaye a gabashin Ukraine da ke fama da yaki sun fara shirin tsagaita wuta "cikakke da cikakke" wanda aka shirya zai fara da tsakar dare, wani mataki da jami'ai ke fatan zai iya haifar da karin matakai don warware rikicin da ya shafe shekaru 6.
Jami'an 'yan tawayen sun ce a ranar Lahadi sun sanar da dakarunsu game da tsagaita wuta kuma sun bayar da dokar hana amfani da makamai.
Sojojin Ukraine sun ce dakarunsu "sun fara shirye-shirye" don tsagaita wuta.
Idan aka tabbatar da shi, zai "buɗe hanya don aiwatar da wasu sassan" na yarjejeniyar zaman lafiya ta Minsk, ofishin shugaban Ukraine ya ce a farkon wannan makon, yana kiran tsagaita wuta "ci gaba".
A shekarar 2015 Faransa da Jamus ne suka shiga tsakani, shirin zaman lafiya na Minsk ya yi nufin warware rikicin da ke tsakanin Ukraine da 'yan tawaye da Rasha ke goyon baya wanda ya barke a shekarar 2014 bayan da Rasha ta mamaye Crimea da kuma goyon bayanta ga 'yan tawaye.
Tun daga lokacin, an kashe mutane fiye da 14,000 a wannan yaƙi.
Shugabannin Rasha da Ukraine sun yaba da yarjejeniyar tsagaita wuta a wata hira ta waya a ranar Lahadi kuma sun jaddada mahimmancin aiwatar da yarjejeniyar da aka cimma a taron kolin Disamba a Paris.
Shugaban Rasha Vladimir Putin ya nuna damuwa game da kiran da Kiev ta yi na sake duba yarjejeniyar Minsk kuma ya ce "matsayin shugaban Ukraine Volodymyr Zelenskiy game da rashin madadin yarjejeniyar Minsk, wanda aka sake bayyana a wannan kiran, ya kamata ya zama ainihin aiki", in ji Kremlin.
Zelenskiy a nasa bangaren, ya jaddada bukatar "ƙarin matakai na zahiri" da nufin sakin 'yan Ukrainian da 'yan tawayen suka tsare a gabashin Ukraine, a yankin Crimea da aka mamaye da Rasha, a cewar wata sanarwa daga ofishinsa.
Yarjejeniyar ta 2015 ta tanadi cewa Ukraine za ta iya dawo da iko kan iyakarta da Rasha a yankunan da 'yan tawaye ke rike da su bayan an ba su babban iko da gudanar da zaben gari.
Yarjejeniyar ta taimaka wajen rage yawan tashin hankali, amma sojojin Ukraine da 'yan tawaye sun ci gaba da musayar harsashin bindigogi da bindigogi.
A watan Disamba, shugabannin Ukraine, Rasha, Faransa da Jamus sun gana a birnin Paris domin sake tattaunawar, inda suka nuna goyon bayansu ga yarjejeniyar Minsk kuma suka amince da sake farfado da zaman lafiya.
Zelenskiy, wanda ya lashe zaben 2019 a kan alkawuran kawo karshen rikicin, yana son Ukraine ta fara sarrafa kan iyakarta kafin zaben kananan hukumomi, amma Kremlin ya dage cewa ya kamata a aiwatar da yarjejeniyar ba tare da sake dubawa ba.
Sabon yarjejeniyar tsagaita wuta da aka cimma a ranar Laraba ta hanyar mambobin kungiyar tuntubar bangarori uku da ta hada da wakilan Rasha, Ukraine da kungiyar tsaro da hadin gwiwa a Turai, kuma jami'an EU sun yi maraba da ita.
A lokacin da yake yin albarka a ranar Lahadi a dandalin St. Peter, Paparoma Francis ya yaba da tsagaita wuta, ya kara da cewa ana bukatar a aiwatar da shi ′′don sake gina amincewa da shimfida tushe don sulhu da ake bukata da kuma dadewa da ake jira tare da mutane.′′
Ciwon zuciya: Cin cakulan sau ɗaya a mako zai rage haɗarin kamuwa da wannan cuta mai sa mutuwa
Wani sabon bincike ya nuna cewa yin wasu abubuwa da suka dace zai iya taimaka wa jijiyoyin zuciya.
Kuma ta yaya zai rage haɗarin ciwon zuciya?
Masu bincike sun yi bincike a kan cututtukan zuciya da ke shafar zuciya da ke kama da ciwon zuciya (CHD) da suka shafe shekaru hamsin.
Cutar zuciya ta zuciya, wadda ake kira cututtukan zuciya na zuciya, tana da alamomi uku: ciwon kirji (angina), ciwon zuciya da kuma ciwon zuciya.
Sauran alamun cutar sun haɗa da bugun zuciya da kuma numfashi.
"Cakulan yana ɗauke da abinci mai gina jiki mai kyau ga zuciya kamar flavonoids, methylxanthines, polyphenols da stearic acid waɗanda za su iya rage kumburi da kuma ƙara cholesterol mai kyau".
Kolesterol mai kyau, wanda ake kira high-density lipoprotein (HDL), yana tara "mummunan" cholesterol - irin wanda ke ratsa jijiyoyin zuciya - kuma yana kai shi hanta.
A cikin hanta, ana raba "mummunan" cholesterol (lipoprotein mai ƙarancin yawa) kuma a fitar da shi daga jiki.
Duk da haka, sabon binciken bai bincika girman rabo ba, ko irin cakulan da aka more.
Ba a san ko mahalarta sun ci cakulan mai duhu ba, cakulan madara ko wasu kayan zaki na koko.
An yi wannan binciken ne bisa bincike da aka yi a dā da ya nuna cewa shan koko (da ke cikin cakulan) yana rage haɗarin ciwon zuciya.
Masana kimiyya sun yi imanin cewa flavonoids da ke cikin cakulan na rage hawan jini da inganta aikin jijiyoyin jini.
Aikin jijiyoyin jini yana nufin yadda jini yake kawo iskar oxygen da abubuwan gina jiki a jiki kuma yana kawar da shara.
Game da sabon binciken, ba a nuna abubuwan da ke haifar da salon rayuwa a sakamakon ba.
Dokta Alice Lichtenstein ta yi bayani a kan wannan binciken, ta ce waɗanda suka yarda cewa suna cin cakulan suna iya samun "mafificiyar nauyi".
Ta daɗa cewa za su iya "yin motsa jiki a kai a kai" kuma "ba za su riƙa damuwa sosai ba".
Ta ci gaba: "Kowane abu zai iya shafan lafiyar zuciya da jijiyoyin jini".
