Sama da mutane miliyan 13.85 da suka kamu da cutar coronavirus a Indiya zuwa yanzu, mutum 32,063 sun mutu, 63.91% na murmurewa
A total an warke mutane 8,85,577 kuma adadin warkewar ya kai kashi 63.91.
New Delhi: Indiya ta ba da rahoton mutane 48,661 da suka kamu da cutar coronavirus a cikin awanni 24 da suka gabata, wanda ya kai jimlar mutane 13,85,522 zuwa yanzu, kamar yadda bayanan gwamnati suka nuna.
Yawan wadanda suka mutu ya karu zuwa 32,063, tare da mutuwar 705 a cikin awanni 24 da suka gabata.
Yawan masu dauke da cutar coronavirus ya ninka kusan makonni uku tun daga ranar 2 ga watan Yuli, lokacin da kasar ta zarce maki miliyan shida.
Adadin COVID na kasar ya kai miliyan 10 a ranar Juma'ar da ta gabata.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, an samu sabbin kamuwa da cutar kusan lakh uku. Wannan ita ce rana ta huɗu a jere da adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 ya karu da sama da 45,000.
Maharashtra a ranar Asabar ta ba da rahoton sabbin mutane 9,251 da suka kamu da COVID-19, wanda ya kai jimlar adadin a jihar zuwa 3,66,368 yayin da mutuwar ta karu da 257, gami da 116 a yankin Mumbai Metropolitan (MMR), zuwa 13,389, in ji ma'aikatar lafiya ta jihar.
An sallami marasa lafiya 7,227 a ranar, wanda ya kai adadin wadanda suka warke zuwa 2,07,194.
Kimanin mutane miliyan 8.85 ne suka warke zuwa yanzu; yawan masu warkewa ya kai kashi 63.91 a safiyar yau.
Adadin masu cutar - yawan marasa lafiyar da suka kamu da cutar coronavirus - ya kai kashi 11.
A farkon wannan makon, gwamnati ta ce tana da burin rage adadin masu cutar zuwa kashi 5.
Karnataka a ranar Asabar ta yi rajistar sabbin cututtukan coronavirus sama da 5,000 a rana ta uku a jere, ta ɗauki jimlar ta wuce 90,000.
Bangalore kadai ta ba da rahoton sabbin shari'o'i 2,036 wanda ya kai jimillar ta zuwa 43,503.
Delhi ta inganta matsayinta a cikin adadin masu dauke da cutar COVID-19 kuma a halin yanzu tana matsayi na takwas a tsakanin jihohi da yankuna a kasar, in ji Babban Ministan Arvind Kejriwal a ranar Asabar.
A cikin mafi girman adadin mutane a rana guda, Kerala a ranar Asabar ta ba da rahoton sabbin sabbin mutane 1,103 da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 wanda ya kai adadin kamuwa da cutar zuwa 18,098, yayin da sama da mutane miliyan 1.5 ke karkashin sa ido.
