Mrs Rooney ta nemi David Sherborne ya yi yaki da zargin da ta yi wa Mrs Vardy
Bayan tattaunawar tsakanin WAGs ta gaza, masu ruwa da tsaki suna tsammanin zanga-zangar ban mamaki
Coleen Rooney ta dauki shahararren lauya mai wakiltar Johnny Depp a shari'ar cin mutuncinsa ta cin gashin kai don wakiltar ta a shari'ar "Wagatha Christie" da Rebekah Vardy.
Jaridar Mail ta fahimci cewa Mrs Rooney ta umarci David Sherborne da ya yi yaki da ikirarin cewa ta bata sunan Mrs Vardy da zargin cewa an fitar da bayanan sirri daga asusunta na Instagram zuwa wata jarida.
Labarin ya zo ne kwanaki bayan da takardun da aka gabatar a kotun koli suka yi ikirarin cewa Mrs Vardy, wacce ke da aure ga dan wasan Leicester City Jamie Vardy, ya sha wahala ta jiki da ta tunani sakamakon zargin Mrs Rooney.
Jaridun sun ce matar mai shekara 38 da haihuwa, wadda mahaifiyar yara biyar ce "ta sha wahala daga matsanancin tsoro da damuwa da ke nuna tsoro na barin gida", kuma ta daɗa cewa an kai Mrs. Vardy, wadda take da ciki wata bakwai a lokacin, "asibiti sau uku... domin ta sha wahala daga tashin hankali sakamakon aikawar da kuma sakamakon hakan".
Baya ga wakiltar Depp a karar da ya shigar kan jaridar The Sun kan zargin da ake yi masa na cin zarafin matarsa, Mr Sherborne, mai shekara 50, yana wakiltar Duke da Duchess na Sussex a karar da suka shigar kan masu wallafa jaridar The Mail on Sunday.
Bayan tattaunawar sasantawa tsakanin WAGs biyu ta gaza, masu ruwa da tsaki yanzu suna tsammanin wani mummunan zanga-zanga a kotu.
"Idan kun yi tunanin shari'ar Depp ta kasance ofishin akwatin, kada ku raina wannan yakin da ke tafe na WAG", in ji wata majiya.
"Yanzu da gaske yaki ne, Coleen ba za ta ja da baya ba, haka ma Becky ba za ta yi ba, za a yi abin mamaki".
Mrs Rooney ta yi ikirarin cewa wani da ke amfani da asusun Instagram na Mrs Vardy ya fallasa labaran karya game da ita ga wata jarida.
An yi mata laƙabi da "Wagatha Christie" bayan ta bayyana yadda ta shafe watanni biyar tana rage yawan abokai da za su iya ganin sabuntawar ta a labaran Instagram har sai da asusun Mrs. Vardy ne kawai ya rage.
Mrs Rooney ta yi ikirarin cewa sai ta wallafa labarin karya a Instagram, wanda daga baya aka buga a wata jarida mai jan fata.
A cikin takardar da ta gabatar, Mrs Vardy, wacce ta musanta hannu, ta yi ikirarin cewa an sa ta ji kamar "zaki mai zunubi" bayan da Mrs Rooney ta wallafa zargin "ta hanyar da aka yi la'akari da gangan wanda aka tsara don haifar da mummunar cutar da kuma damuwa mai tsanani".
Amma kungiyar Mrs Rooney ta kalubalanci ikirarin, tana zargin cewa bayanan da ke tattare da wahalarta "aikin PR ne" wanda ke jan hankali daga abubuwan da suka faru.
Wata majiya ta ce: "Takardu na Becky suna nunawa ne, duk abin da yake ƙarya ne".
Mrs Rooney - wacce ke da 'ya'ya hudu da tsohon tauraron Ingila Wayne Rooney - lauya Paul Lunt, na kamfanin lauyoyi na Brabners da ke Liverpool ne ke wakiltarta.
Mrs Vardy tana aiki da kamfanin Kingsley Napley na London, amma ba a san ko ta riga ta ba da umarnin lauya ba.
Mai magana da yawun Mrs Rooney ya ki yin tsokaci.
