An Ba Abdulrashid Maina Kyautar Biyan Kudin Kaura.
Kotun Tarayya da ke Abuja ta ba Abdulrashid Maina belin ranar 26 ga Nuwamba, 2019, a karkashin Alkali Okon Abang, amma rashin cika sharuddan bayar da belin ya haifar da tsare shi a tsare.
