Mazi ya kara da cewa ba a sake shi ba har sai an kammala wasu takardu da ka'idojin aiki, sannan aka sake shi, kuma cewa abokin harka yanzu yana zaune tare da danginsa.
Ya ce za a ci gaba da shari'ar a watan Satumba lokacin da kotu za ta dawo daga hutu.
A ranar 25 ga watan Oktoba, 2019, EFCC ta gurfanar da Abdulrashid Maina, tare da dansa Faisal da wani kamfani mai suna Common Input Property and Investment Ltd a gaban babbar kotun tarayya da ke Abuja a karkashin Alkalin Okon Abang, inda suke fuskantar zargin cin hanci da rashawa da karbar cin hanci da rashawa sama da naira biliyoyin.
