Mubarak Abba, daya daga cikin matasan da suka kafa wannan shiri, ya ce daga yanzu ba za su kara jiran gwamnati ta samar da irin wadannan ayyuka ba.
Nawa ne kudin kammala aikin?
Mubarak Abba ya ce sun gudanar da wasu ayyukan ci gaban al'umma amma wannan shine mafi girma da suka yi.
Ana sa ran aikin zai ci kusan Naira miliyan biyar.
Hanyar da ake samun kudin aikin ita ce mutanen yankin suna tara kudi daga juna ta yadda kowa zai bayar da duk abin da Allah ya ba shi domin gudanar da wannan aikin.
Wannan a cewar Muhsin Aminu Dukawa wanda ke tara kudade domin aikin.
Iyaye mata ma suna ba da gudummawarsu ga aikin.
Iyayen mata ba su bar baya ba, su ma suna da nasu bangaren.
Hajia Fadima Danbalarabe da aka fi sani da Niniya tana daya daga cikin irin wadannan uwaye a yankin.
Ta ce suna ba ma'aikatan abinci da sabulu don su wanke kansu bayan sun gama aiki da kuma duk wani abin da Allah ya tanadar musu.
Yaya dattawan yankin suka ji game da aikin?
Matasan da suka jagoranci aikin sun ce aikin ya yiwu ne kawai tare da taimakon shugabannin unguwanni na gida da dattawan al'umma.
Alhaji Lamin Isah, daya daga cikin dattawan yankin, ya ce wannan matsalar ta kasance matsala na dogon lokaci, amma yanzu 'ya'yansu suna magance matsalar kuma suna iya magance ta.
Kamar yadda rukunin suna da hannu a harkokin addini, haka ma matasa sun sa shugabannin addinai na yankin su kasance a gaba wajen tallafa wa wannan aikin.
Gwani Hadi Sadisu Zangon Bare-bari sanannen malamin Alkur'ani ne a Kano wanda ke cikin wannan aiki.
Ya ce yana farin ciki matasan yankin sun zo wurinsa kuma sun nemi ya ba su shawara kan aikin.
Yaya al'ummar yankin suke ɗaukan aikin?
'Yan kishin kasa sun ce wannan shi ne abin da ya kamata kowace al'umma ta ci gaba da yi don kawo ci gaba a yankunansu.
Alhaji Abubakar Ibrahim wanda aka fi sani da Gwamnati Ikon Allah yana daya daga cikin masu kishin kasa a Kano.
Muna kira ga sauran matasa da su bi misalin wadannan unguwannin domin idan muka tsaya muna jiran gwamnati ta yi hakan, za mu jira ba tare da an gama ba kuma ba za a yi gyaran ba.
Masu sharhi kan al'amuran yau da kullun sun daɗe suna kalubalantar gwamnati kan yadda kusan kowane unguwa ke fama da irin waɗannan matsalolin, kuma gwamnati ta kasa gyara su, kuma yanzu ta kai ga matakin da jama'a suka fara ɗaukar irin wannan matakin don yin gyaran kansu.
Har yanzu 'yan Najeriya na fuskantar mawuyacin hali.
Gwamnatin Tarayya ta Najeriya da jihohi sun ce sun kashe biliyoyin naira don tallafawa marasa galihu, don rage wahalar da cutar COVID-19 da aka sani da coronavirus ta haifar.
Ahmad Tukur Jada, daya daga cikin shugabannin kungiyoyin kananan manoma a Najeriya, ya bayyana wa sashen Hausa kalubalen da talakawa ke fuskanta a wannan lokacin annobar, ciki har da tsadar rayuwa.
Game da batun tallafin corona, ya ce ba su ga komai ba.
Amma yayin da talakawa ke gwagwarmaya, wasu jami'ai da kungiyoyi sun riga sun nemi hanyoyin tallafawa, don rage wahalar al'umma.
Dan majalisar dokokin jihar Taraba Bashir Muhammad Bape ya shaida wa Muryar Amurka cewa a mazabarsa ta Nguroje, sun sayi babura 60 da injinan niƙa da na'urorin dinki da aka rarraba wa mutane don su iya samun abin rayuwa.
Ya zuwa yanzu, an bude wasu kasuwanni a jihar Taraba amma akwai gwagwarmaya kan gaskiyar cewa farashin wasu kayayyaki na asali kamar hatsi da karafa waɗanda ke da babban buƙata suna ƙaruwa.
Na fuskanci kalubale kafin na gano wanda zai gaje ni wato Shettima.
Tsohon Gwamnan Jihar Borno kuma Sanata mai wakiltar Borno ta Tsakiya a Majalisar Dattawan Najeriya, Alhaji Kashim Shettima, ya bayyana dalla-dalla kalubalen da ya fuskanta kafin ya iya gano zababben Gwamnan Jihar Borno, Farfesa Babagana Umara Zulum, a matsayin magajinsa a kujerar gwamnan jihar da zai bar kamar yadda zaben 2019 ya nuna.
Shettima ya sanar da hakan ne yayin da yake gabatar da jawabi a kungiyar kungiyoyin matasa a Birnin Kebbi, babban birnin jihar Kebbi, mai taken "Matasa da ci gaban iyali: Misalai daga Arewa Mai Girma".
"Gwamna Babagana Zulum mutum ne mai juriya fiye da ni, kuma zabarsa a matsayin magaji ba batun fifiko bane na mutum, amma na mutanen jihar Borno baki daya", in ji shi.
A wannan bangaren ma, tsohon gwamnan ya shawarci shugabannin Najeriya da kada su manta cewa iko amana ce da Allah Sarki ya ba mutum, ya kara da cewa, "kuma ku dauka a matsayin batun lokaci, kuma a ranar shari'a za a tambaye ku game da duk abin da kuka yi a wannan lokacin ".
A matsayinka na shugaba, dole ne ka san cewa kai abin koyi ne, kuma ya dace mu ilimantar da matasa don nan gaba, domin ba za mu iya kasancewa a nan har abada ba.
Bugu da kari, Sanata Shettima ya yi tir da yadda wasu daga cikin mutanen da ke da goyon bayan iko ke amfani da damar su, kuma ya kara da cewa, wannan yana da alaƙa da sha'awar iko.
A gefe guda kuma, ya nuna damuwa game da yadda wasu matasa suke rayuwa ba tare da manufa ba saboda rashin ilimi ko damar yin aiki da kansu.
Ya nuna cewa akwai bukatar matasa su yi kokari don ilimi, wanda shi kadai zai ba su damar da za su bunkasa kasar zuwa mafi girma.
Hakazalika, Shettima ya kuma yi kira da a inganta matakan cikin gida don bunkasa tattalin arziki da rage matsalolin rashin aikin yi a kasar baki daya.
Likitan tawagar Ukraine, mai shekaru 48, ya mutu sakamakon cutar coronavirus
Anton Hudaev, likitan tawagar kwallon kafa ta kasar Ukraine, ya mutu sakamakon cutar coronavirus mai shekaru 48, kungiyar kwallon kafa ta cikin gida (UAF) ta ce.
"A madadin Shugaban Kungiyar Kwallon Kafa ta Ukraine Andriy Pavelka, babban kocin tawagar Andriy Shevchenko da kuma dukkanin dangin kwallon kafa na Ukraine, muna mika ta'aziyyarmu ga danginsa", in ji UAF a cikin wata sanarwa.
"Dukan tawagar 'yan wasan kasar na cikin babban bakin ciki".
Hudaev kuma likitan kungiyar ne na kungiyar Metalist Kharkiv ta gida.
Kwayar cutar ta kashe mutane sama da 1,600 a Ukraine, wanda ya ba da rahoton kusan kamuwa da cutar 65,000.
An tabbatar da ficewar Pedro daga Chelsea yayin da abokan wasan sa suka yi 'serenade' a gaban sa a dakin canja kaya
Kocin Chelsea Frank Lampard ya girmama dan wasan waje Pedro Rodriguez bayan da ya buga wasan karshe a gasar da kulob din a ranar Lahadi.
Dan wasan mai shekara 32 ya rubuta wani karin lokaci a kwantiraginsa don ganin kakar wasa tare da kungiyar amma zai koma AS Roma a kan kyauta kyauta bayan kammala yakin.
Dan wasan na kasar Spain, wanda ya zo daga Barcelona a shekarar 2015, ya taka rawar gani a karkashin Lampard a wannan kakar wasa tare da farawa takwas kawai a Premier League da kuma wasanni 21 a dukkan gasa.
Shugaban Blues ya tabbatar da ficewar Pedro bayan kungiyar da ke yammacin Landan ta rufe ta farko a cikin hudu tare da nasara 2-0 akan Wolves, tare da tsohon soja yana fitowa daga benci don bayyanarsa ta karshe.
"Pedro ya buga wasan karshe a kungiyar", Lampard ya shaida wa Sky Sports.
"Yaran sun yi masa waka a cikin ɗakin canza tufafi kuma daidai ne saboda aikin da ya yi a gaba ɗaya da kuma wannan kulob din.
"Wannan ne wasan karshe da ya buga a gasar Premier, amma tasirin da ya yi a nan yana da girma.
Ina so in gode wa likitocin yara da kuma yi masa fatan alheri yayin da yake ci gaba.
"Zai kasance a nan har zuwa sauran wasannin, amma babban dan wasan kulob din ya tafi kuma ruhun kulob din da na gani bayan haka ya kasance na musamman".
Pedro ya wallafa sakon ban kwana bayan wasan ta shafinsa na Twitter, yana rubuta: "Wasan karshe a Stamford Bridge.
Na gode wa duk masoya don goyon bayan da kuka bayar a tsawon shekaru, ga kulob din da ya ba ni damar zama Blue da kuma abokan aiki na.
Za ka kasance a cikin zuciyata har abada.
Yanzu bari mu yi gwagwarmaya don kofin FA !!!
Babban iyali mai launin shuɗi. "
Tsohon dan wasan Barcelona ya bar kungiyar bayan ya taimaka wa Chelsea tun lokacin da ta lashe kofin a shekarar 2017 a karkashin Antonio Conte kuma ta lashe kofin FA a shekarar 2018, da kuma gasar Europa League shekara guda bayan haka a karkashin Maurizio Sarri.
An ga wani mai kamun kifi yana jefa kwalbar giya a kan hatsi a Devon
Wani mai kamun kifi ya jefa kwalbar giya a kan wata hatimi lokacin da ta katse masa aikin kamun kifi, wata kungiya mai ba da agaji ta ce.
Hotunan da aka dauka a Hope's Nose, kusa da Torquay, sun nuna wani mutum yana jefa makami a kan dabbar daga dutse.
Duncan Kenny, wanda ya dauki hotunan, ya ce, wannan kifi yana farauta lokacin da mai kamun kifi ya zubar da kwalbar kuma ya jefa shi, ya buge dabbar a baya.
Mista Kenny ya kira shi "abin kunya da rashin hankali".
Ya ce yana tattara shara a wurin shakatawa na Devon tare da mambobin kungiyar kare lafiyar Seal Project lokacin da ya ga harin a safiyar Lahadi.
"The hatimi sanya wani ƙoƙari don samun kama kifi line", ya ce.
"Mai kamun kifi ya gama shan giya, ya zubar da kwalbar kuma ya jefa ta a kan hatimi.
"Foshin ya buga hatimi a baya kuma ya yi iyo".
Mista Kenny ya ce "alhamdulillahi haruffa halittu ne masu ƙarfi", amma ya ce haruffa kawai suna yin abin da ke cikin yanayinsu.
Ya ce: "Ta wajen jefa masa kwalban gilashi, kana hana shi farauta.
The Seal Project ya ce "ba wani yanayi ne na musamman ba" kuma ya karɓi "ra'ayoyi da yawa game da wannan halin tashin hankali kwanan nan".
A wani sakon Facebook, ta ce masu sa kai sun tattara buhunan shara 12 a lokacin ziyarar da suka yi a Hope's Nose a ranar Lahadi kuma sun lura da "misalai da yawa na rashin zamantakewa".
