Da alama jam'iyyar adawa ta fara tasiri a kan magoya bayanta, a cewar Ramatou Alele, daya daga cikin masu fafatawa a Jam'iyyar MPN Patriotic Movement.
Za a iya cewa an yi shiri sosai don zaben, wanda zai fara a watan Disamba, tare da rahotanni da ke nuna cewa hukumomin Nijar sun fara kokarin ba da aikin shirya jerin sunayen masu jefa kuri'a na kasar ga Kungiyar Faransanci ta Duniya, wani mataki a cikin tsarin buga takardun zabe.
