Wani mutum ya samu raunuka da za su iya sauya rayuwarsa bayan wasu mutane uku sun kai masa hari a Edinburgh.
An kai wa wanda aka kashe hari mai tsanani a titin Drum, a yankin Gilmerton, tsakanin karfe 23:00 da 23:30 a ranar Asabar.
'Yan sanda a Scotland sun ce an kai shi asibitin Royal da raunuka masu tsanani.
Det Con Dale Miles, jami'in da ke kula da binciken, ya ce: "Wannan hari ne na mugunta da ba a yi niyya ba".
Wadanda ake zargi sun gudu zuwa titin Newtoft.
An bayyana daya a matsayin mutum a cikin shekaru 30, mai tsayin kafa 1,80 da kuma tsoka.
Yana da gajeren gashi mai duhu kuma yana sanye da fararen fata, wando mai duhu da takalma masu duhu.
