CORONA: Mutane 137 sun kamu da cutar Corona a Najeriya a ranar Talata.
Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Kasa (NCDC) ta sanar da karin mutane 137 da suka kamu da cutar coronavirus a Najeriya a ranar Talata.
Alkaluman da NCDC ta fitar a ranar Talata sun nuna cewa jihar Legas tana da karin mutane 60, Abia-21, FCT-18, Rivers-13, Kaduna-5, Oyo-4, Edo-3, Delta-2, Imo-2, Kano-2, Ogun-2, Bauchi-1, Gombe-1, Nasarawa-1 Niger-1 da Osun-1.
Ya zuwa yanzu mutane 63,173 sun kamu da cutar a Najeriya, 59,634 sun warke, kuma 1,151 sun mutu.
Bayan haka wasu mutane 2,375 suka kamu da cutar a Najeriya.
Jihar Legas har yanzu tana da mafi yawan wadanda suka kamu da cutar, tare da mutane 21,398, FCT -6,142, Oyo -3,456, Edo -2,669, Delta -1,816, Rivers 2,844, Kano -1,749, Ogun -2,053, Kaduna -2,663, Katsina -953, Ondo -1,669, Borno -745, Gombe -938, Bauchi -713, Ebonyi -1,049, Plateau -3,652, Enugu -1,314, Abia -898, Imo -619, Jigawa -1,065, Kwara -329, Bayelsa -413, Nasarawa -483, Osun -0,93 Sokoto -165, Niger -277, Akwa Ibom -295, Benue -493, Adamawa -252, Anambra -277, Kebbi -93, Zamfara -79, Yobe -79, Adamawa -259, Ekiti -335.
Yana yiwuwa mutum da ya kamu da cutar Corona ya samu matsalar rashin lafiyar kwakwalwa.
Likitoci a Jami'ar Kolejin UCL a Burtaniya sun bayyana cewa yana yiwuwa mutum da ya kamu da cutar Corona zai iya samun matsalolin lafiyar kwakwalwa.
Jagoran wannan binciken kuma jami'in UCL Ross Paterson ya sanar da cewa ya zama dole a yi karin bincike don sanin girman raunin da cutar za ta iya haifar wa mutum.
Cutar kwayar cutar Corona tana ɗaya daga cikin ƙwayoyin cuta da ke haifar da mutum ya kamu da sanyi, wanda, idan mai tsanani, zai iya haifar da wahala daga wahalar numfashi, wanda ake kira Ciwon Numfashi na Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS-CoV), da kuma mummunan cuta wanda zai iya toshe makogwaro.
Amma Corona Virus sabuwar cuta ce wacce ba a taba samun ta a jikin mutum ba.
Alamomin kamuwa da cuta sun hada da matsaloli tare da hanyoyin numfashi a cikin makogwaro watau numfashi, zazzabi mai zafi, tari mai tsanani, da ciwon makogwaro.
Idan ciwon yana da tsanani, zai iya sa mutum ya daina numfashi, sai kuma ya kamu da ciwon huhu, kuma idan ciwon ya yi tsanani sosai, sai kodan mutumin su daina aiki gaba ɗaya.
Akwai wasu matakan gaggawa da zasu taimaka wajen kauce wa wannan kamuwa da cuta, kamar wanke hannuwan sau da yawa da sabulu da ruwa, da kuma rufe hanci da baki a koyaushe lokacin yin fitsari.
Kuma a tsabtace nama da ƙwai sosai kafin a ci su.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta bukaci mutane su nisanta kansu da duk wanda ke nuna alamun rashin lafiya, musamman wadanda aka lissafa a sama, kuma su je asibiti nan da nan don samun magani idan ba ku da lafiya.
Daruruwan Masu Zanga-Zanga Sun Tattara A Birnin LA A Cikin Haɗin Kai Da Masu Zanga-zangar Portland
LOS ANGELES (CBSLA) - Kimanin masu zanga-zanga 300 sun taru a tsakiyar garin Los Angeles a ranar Asabar da yamma don tallafawa wata motsi na tsawon watanni biyu a Portland, Oregon, inda jami'an tilasta bin doka na tarayya ke karkashin dubawa bayan rikice-rikice da masu zanga-zanga.
An yi irin wannan gangamin a duk fadin Amurka a Boston, Chicago, Cleveland, New York da sauran biranen.
Kungiyoyin 'Yan Tawaye da Fashinism da kuma 'Yan Matasa na' Yancin 'Yan Matasa ne suka shirya zanga-zangar a L.A.
Jama'a sun yi tafiya zuwa hedkwatar 'yan sanda na Los Angeles a tituna na farko da Main, sannan zuwa Cibiyar Kula da 'Yan Sanda ta Metropolitan.
Masu halarta kuma sun koma Alameda offamp na 101 Freeway, amma daga baya suka tafi.
An ga wasu daga cikin mutanen da ke cikin kungiyar suna fasa tagogin ginin tarayya da ke tsakiyar gari kuma an rubuta alamun tarayya da kalmomin batanci.
Akalla an kama mutum daya a lokacin zanga-zangar.
An Kama Uba da Ɗa da Kimanin Ru'ya'yan Ruwa Miliyan 1.54 A Mizoram
An yi safarar maganin Heroin, wanda ya kai kimanin Rs 1.55 crore a kasuwar gida, daga Myanmar: 'Yan sanda
An kama wani mutum da dansa da kilo 1.9 na maganin sauro a gundumar Hnahthial ta Mizoram kusa da iyakar Myanmar, in ji 'yan sanda a ranar Lahadi.
An ce an shigo da maganin Heroin da darajarsa ta kai Rs 1.55 crore a kasuwar kasar daga Myanmar.
An kama Duhkima (62) da dansa Remthangpuia (33) tare da miyagun kwayoyi a daren Juma'a daga kauyen Ngharchhip, in ji 'yan sanda.
Sun kuma sauke kimanin gram 280 na maganin kashe kwayoyi, wanda yakai kimanin Rs 15 lakh, yayin da suke iyo a fadin kogi yayin da suke kokarin tserewa daga 'yan sanda, in ji jami'ai.
A cewar 'yan sanda, an yi imanin cewa wannan kwace ita ce mafi girma a cikin jihar.
An tuhumi wadanda ake zargi a karkashin sassan da suka dace na Dokar Narcotic Drugs & Psychotropic Substances (NDPS) ta 1985.
Ko da yake iyakokin jihohi da wanda ke tare da Myanmar sun kasance a rufe saboda barkewar cutar coronavirus, safarar kwayoyi da sauran kayayyakin da aka yi da gangan sun ci gaba ba tare da raguwa ba, in ji majiyoyin 'yan sanda.
Assam Rifles kwanan nan ta kama manyan motoci 25 dauke da goro, wanda aka kiyasta kimanin Rs 4 crore, ana safarar su daga Myanmar, in ji su.
Mick Fleetwood ya girmama Peter Green: 'Waƙar sa za ta ci gaba da rayuwa'
Mick Fleetwood ya ba da ladabi ga Peter Green, wanda ya kafa Fleetwood Mac, wanda ya mutu a yau yana da shekaru 73.
Green ya kasance memba na asali na ƙungiyar dutsen mai suna, tare da Mick da aka ambata a sama, da kuma Jeremy Spencer.
Duk da barin ƙungiyar a cikin 1970 kafin manyan nasarorin su tare da kundin waƙoƙi kamar Rumours, Mick ya ba da ladabi ga tsohon abokin aikinsa, yana tabbatar wa magoya baya cewa "waƙar sa za ta ci gaba da rayuwa".
Fleetwood ya fada wa PA: "A gare ni, da kowane memba na Fleetwood Mac na yanzu da na yanzu, rasa Peter Green abu ne mai ban mamaki.
"Peter shi ne mutumin da ya kafa ƙungiyar Fleetwood Mac tare da ni, John McVie, da Jeremy Spencer.
Babu wanda ya taɓa shiga cikin Fleetwood Mac ba tare da girmamawa ga Peter Green da basirarsa ba, kuma ga gaskiyar cewa kiɗa ya kamata ya haskaka haske kuma koyaushe ya ba da sha'awar rashin daidaituwa. "
Wannan ɗan shekara 73 ya ƙara da cewa: "Peter, zan yi kewarka, amma ka yi haƙuri kiɗanka yana nan da rai.
Na gode maka da ka tambaye ni in zama mai buga maka ƙwallo shekaru da yawa da suka wuce.
Mun yi kyau, kuma mun kafa tafarki mai ban sha'awa na waƙa don mutane da yawa su ji daɗi.
"Allah ya sa ka yi sa'a, abokina mafi soyuwa... ina son Mick Fleetwood".
Da yake tabbatar da mutuwar Green, wata sanarwa daga lauyoyin Swan Turton ta karanta: "Da matukar bakin ciki ne dangin Peter Green suka sanar da mutuwarsa a karshen wannan makon, cikin kwanciyar hankali a barcinsa.
"Za a bayar da ƙarin bayani a cikin kwanaki masu zuwa".
Green ya bar 'yarsa, Rosebud Samuels-Greenbaum, wanda ta raba tare da tsohon matarsa Jane Samuels.
Green ya kafa Fleetwood Mac tare da abokan aikinsa Mick Fleetwood da Jeremy Spencer, tare da ƙungiyar da aka kira Peter Green's Fleetwood Mac tare da Jeremy Spencer.
Koyaya, mawaƙin-waƙar zai bar ƙungiyar a cikin 1970, bayan kundin waƙoƙi huɗu.
Fleetwood Mac za ta ci gaba da samun babban yabo da sanannen duniya tare da ƙarin layi ciki har da Lindsey Buckingham da Stevie Nicks a kan kundin kundin ciki har da Rumours da Tusk.
Magu ya kalubalanci rahoton kwamitin Ayo Salami.
Lauyan shugaban hukumar EFCC da aka dakatar, Ibrahim Magu, ya kalubalanci rahoton da Hukumar Ayo Salami ta fitar da shawarar cewa shugaban kasar ya cire shi don a gurfanar da shi a gaban kotu.
Wahab Shitu, lauyan Ibrahim Magu ya ce har yanzu bai gama tattara bayanan da za a gabatar ba, duk da jin korafin da kwamitin Salami ya yi.
Ya kara da cewa a sakamakon zargin da aka yi wa shugaban hukumar yaki da cin hanci da rashawa, kwamitin bai fitar da kwafin tuhumar da ake yi masa ba.
Shittu ya kara da cewa a matsayinsa na lauyan Ibrahim Magu, har yanzu bai samu damar ganin tuhume-tuhume da sauran zarge-zargen da ake yi wa Magu ba.
